It's a refreshing detour from your typical breakfast/brunch diner and in the best way possible. The Chicken Cobb salad was amazing. It was exactly my idea of a well-balanced meal, and I‚Äôd happily eat it any time. The Bulgogi eggs benedict was a hearty recommendation that hit the mark, though I might pair it with a side salad next time to balance things out.
The Americano was a bit watery for my taste, as I prefer a richer, more rounded brew, but the coffee they use is good, as evidenced by the delicious Affogato. Overall, it was a great experience, and I can easily recommend this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOBBQBsBVne7CdspMkJ7s050MLquoxqAvgVE9Z0&fid=0x0:0x997a53630888a21b"],"When":"2024-8-2"},{"Name":"James Shu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-X1zh_92u1cTBADC3dN2MfeBqYQzw8dQmS7J28C0kZ28jdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great brunch place! We‚Äôll definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDU8aoXbh_75qHSir7NAk-kiwBD-O8oLTW_1fU&fid=0x0:0x997a53630888a21b"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Louise Tuck","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzJMFzeKH8Wl8xeVohNuiA2sGD_md3syY7itgjQ1C7izfji6QePA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely delicious!! Parking is a bit limited at the front, but there is some in the back and on the side streets. I had the beef, Bulgogi Benedict and my partner had the chicken and waffles. We also ordered a fruit smoothie to share, but it tasted a bit bitter in my opinion. I like that the chicken and waffles came with fresh fruit. The potatoes were nicely done with the Benedict and my eggs were cooked perfectly. Next time I would love to try the pasta dishes! It is a smaller restaurant so services is quite attentive, but don‚Äôt come with a large party unless you‚Äôre ok sitting separately.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNeYBlhrRePVvrA0j0eg0xMCc-IzqUANFfwVGl&fid=0x0:0x997a53630888a21b"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Lisa koebel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLw6QlYwmHtALujBhkwO4UyMcd7F8x7DlhGdHsr9U0G5Mtg1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"BEST breakfast (I‚Äôm sure lunch and dinners are AMAZING too - but I‚Äôve only ate breakfast there).  Every time we are in town‚Ä¶ we go to Kook‚Äôs Cooks!  It‚Äôs a MUST! I order the Bulgogi Benny.  INSANELY DELICIOUS!  Fast and friendly service makes this a 5/5 EVERY TIME.  Not fancy‚Ä¶ don‚Äôt need it‚Ä¶ I‚Äôd eat their food on a park bench!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPCcZByvgBVPxWlvPe7jqVulpp7g_ReW9fiW8dP&fid=0x0:0x997a53630888a21b"],"When":"2024-8-23"},{"Name":"Arjun Tyagi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWopm7CB27Brsn2nZf_ZcGMYA1rC2xZn0gFS2Ev_B4zUk8mX8MoIQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my 4th time here and I‚Äôve always loved it. Haven‚Äôt had a bad dish from the chicken and waffles to the frittata and pasta. Thankful to have a wonderful breakfast and brunch spot in the neighbourhood.

Their menu is traditional Canadian brunch style with a touch of Asian (Korean) influence from the owners. Having been to South Korea many times in my life the service and fusion flavours are truly unique but give me hints of neat spots I tried on my travels but with a more North American twist. Will definitely keep coming back and continue to spread the word about this fantastic hidden gem.

They have ample parking, cute indoor diner style seating and a nice patio for sunny days outside. The staff are always friendly and attentive and our server on this visit on Tuesday, July 2nd around 1:30 PM - 2:30 PM was absolutely awesome üëè as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPYQdhaTl4-Ll1Fxf4u7XfkHDY3RfZ0QU3OQ64e&fid=0x0:0x997a53630888a21b"],"When":"2024-7-3"},{"Name":"Juliana Bergstrom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9z_V4_T4Kb4r0iN3AY1nc4y5c0skm3bc-4FOsN5--jOSweZ2U=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great coffee and really good food. [{"Name":"Coniah Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRF6exFWLtpR3e9xDEQIA8baJa13bfBk5CzdOsGQJX1lxG9B8F=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A hidden surprise gem!
Came in without any expectations but very pleasantly impressed with the interior.  The food was amazing!  Everything was in balanced.  Truffle Risotto was well cooked with hint of balsamic flavoured mushrooms.  Benedict was creamy and soft.  Seafood linguine was tastefully fusiony spicy.
And the cruffles‚Ä¶ what a fine and delicious to finish off a meal.  And yes‚Ä¶ all the special coffees were good!

Will definitely recommend this place to anyone.

The restaurant is also family friendly- they have special kids menu.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOzA5sKIVZBj7hdzzdx0dAJrQ6A9GlxkEbKK7DC&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Stephie N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd0_eqzaDNFpYKxu_At0QKV_opW1IXDZ3BtSf_D5LFw7-X91jS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôm genuinely surprised this fantastic place isn‚Äôt packed with people. It feels like sitting at a bistro in Paris, with its beautiful patio and ample space. Unlike other popular brunch spots nearby, you don‚Äôt have to overhear conversations from the next table, thanks to the generous spacing between tables. The food was delicious, but I wish the coffee were stronger‚Äîit was a bit too weak for my taste. Even the restrooms are stylish! I‚Äôll definitely be visiting again in the near future.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNIPt9HrlVESQ7NWmlger11SRLVUmi3PzCBp7V8&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-9-20"},{"Name":"Dahee Sim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX9xskvqrMlPhfaEjei8fHc2AKp7yd0SfCkRSHV-khbg0nQPk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A gorgeous mid-century-style interior and great food. Honestly, I was surprised to find a brunch spot like this in Coquitlam. It‚Äôs not too busy. I enjoyed my meal without rushing. Highly recommended for a date spot. I would love to come back and recommend this place to anyone I know.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMe76FYiQnvzBF7kVx5mnkesf4oadu4dy_tlnyD&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-9"},{"Name":"Jenna A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGeR4hbJbNaJlqcXNAxQUrp3QHCCXfRtmHBdhtRlvTl_6ydw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I've visited this restaurant several times and have enjoyed the wonderful ambiance, particularly the patio with its beautiful views. The food is delicious and well-portioned. However, the service quality varies. While most of the staff are courteous, one server was not very friendly and handled things carelessly. With more consistent service, this place could be exceptional.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6B3d3ldgXF0MjORrSBlg1esfRXZTZl94EWzI4&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"K‚Äôs coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dine-in again in August, new menu. Taste is good as usual. Still like it.

Dine-in twice within one week. Very interesting menu. Love their vibes. Service is a bit on the slow side but perfect for me to make up my mind on those interesting dishes. Every dish is a feast for the senses, combining color, aroma, and flavor perfectly. Will definitely return for more. üòãüòãüòã","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPx9tx4IxpQSmwOcmLv8ddhuFNkeLJXAmiPW7VI&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Courtney Pittman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImDRdaEZ1vUaDf3DGIejVTXETr6R1b9106tf3qLHJFMRHijw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It has a nice atmosphere, and is very spacious inside and has outdoor seating with a beautiful view! I went there with 5 adults and 2 kids under 3, it was accommodating for our kids and they have a kids menu and a high chair. I ordered the tomato seafood pasta, it was delicious! And my husband ordered the salmon eggs Benedict, also very yummy! I especially liked the spices they used! The staff was also kind and very quick to help! For example, my child spilled his water, and they cleaned it up for us right away!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgjAY09m6k9cxVOG4Az0WqGpq2fFEdBw-FJImn&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"A Miraji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKbtSn1-d3iEkTDQas0xH_xCGg1PKv8z1hKaZIhPkrsgM_kICp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Loved this place, food was very well prepared and served. The staff were nice, polite and helpful. The place itself is nicely decorated and a appropriate selection of music tracks was playing which made the experience even better. Totally recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMrQC1fF5b3mfJw-XcDL01DLAj6uIxwwrpmTln6&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-12-1"},{"Name":"Ruby E.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTXhvN-EpNac4Qr_mgdf5IDJLY8uKSuinXxuVkhfUtlVyIdrlu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you love bennies, this is your spot!  Spacious with lots of seating and good variety of menu items so there‚Äôs something for everyone, including vegetarian & gluten-free options.  Even though brunch is served all day, some other items aren't available until after 5pm.
The coffee was disappointing. Their $4 coffee was in a cup that held less than 6 oz. The flat white was served in a glass without a handle?! & way too creamy (more like a latte).
The "Sunset mimosa" ($12) we ordered was delicious but we suspect we were served their zero proof mocktail instead the "Sunrise Mimosa" (for the same price) as there was a canned cherry on the bottom. The Espresso martini ($14) was too sweet & creamy, opt for the Carajillo instead if you want more coffee flavor.
Overall, we prefer Pur & Simple for brunch & beverages.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMIRn2r-vEtR6XvTYqjnnBoMAcr3moEk50xhb05&fid=0x0:0x8242b04469c5d5af"],"When":"2024-11-3"}]

[{"Name":"E Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSf46GoVDYA6DwVd9VW9_YDSbB2ZybZwD8Gjg5Qpn6bN0v14Wr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Was lucky to get a table the other night when we were in the neighborhood. Modern ambience, but you can definitely feel the warm Italian hospitality here. Friendly staff and good food. Recommend to book a table.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnhm0MuEeApdX4PY7B_Xhwv6eNgtqcD0gFQtDg&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-10"},{"Name":"P C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL88eGEDtgHkBgqL891vvj7LFnoV5_8VQFpZ1gQaT540IRImA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely fantastic! Customer service was great and food was phenomenal. The prices for Tuesday pasta night were amazing, deals like that for such high quality food are hard to find! Even at full price I definitely recommend checking this spot out for dinner with family or date night.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Lo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPl6fiur4C23qnNmuemdRGEXafuu9PoCts6x4CUY75Jkk5idyUOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had their Hula pizza. I don't really like pizza that much, but That Place's was delightful! It's not quite a Napoleon pizza (puffy, chewy crust), I'm not sure what style it is but I loved it, as it is super thin.

The pineapples that accompanied the cures meats on my pizza were not sour, juicy but not dry, and had a sweetness that paired well with the meat.

Got to try my friend's pizzas as well, and everything we ordered was so delicious. I have to come back for their pasta dishes!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWWN42pLsLaryVZ2ISyc8jvsBx4vKIJP1k6_9g&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-25"},{"Name":"Marie Amin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKR0qp3fose5GsYts0dtMeJqwXo1MWNFSPwo4SjCtJGEbgYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":""First time at THAT PLACE, Went here for dinner with my boys and husband to celebrate his birthday. Great food and amazing service. Highly recommend checking them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOg-CDNNf8gHM4MeYnGtflN94bgoqf6INfVWNcn&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-6-11"},{"Name":"Karen Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6IC1wpFEjyCTx3FWQ_sOYFSAr6w5s8xxxgofCEztXjk_-KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the staff at this place. Vanessa is always so welcoming and a hoot to talk to. It's like that family-owned restaurant in your neighborhood that you keep on wanting to go back to. They make an excellent Caesar salad and our favorites are their Wood-Fired pizzas and of course Pat's cheesecakes!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLGgIU2jvOA6dZo_R-fDScmbPQKFMa9bNbD6fpKC_vMNnPtfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time eating at this restaurant and wow! I ordered their duck fettuccine, and chocolate peanut butter cheesecake both were a 10/10.  I have tried a lot of pasta at many different restaurants (including upscale) and this place was significantly better.  It reminded me of the pasta I ate when in Rome and Florence.

I am a desert person and am very critical of desserts. The chocolate peanut butter cheese cake was airy and the best dessert I had in a long time. It was not dense as your typical cheese cake dessert.

The pasta I ate was very well priced. The wine was well priced and dessert.  The excellent quality and taste for the food for the price is unheard of these days.

The customer service was amazing. I believe it was the owners. They were funny and kind and made the experience even more enjoyable.

Overall, I had a great experience. This will be my go-to pasta place. Only ‚Äúnegative‚Äù  is that this place is 30 minutes from my home. The food I ate was so delicious that I purchased take out for the same order (pasta and dessert) so that I could eat it the next day without driving back‚Ä¶.I‚Äôve never done that before.

Edit: the takeout was not as good for some reason. I would recommend eating in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO0w4UOCi_NGKNz3P-A1Pjm1_xxTI9oMai9fOpN&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2024-4-28"},{"Name":"Michael and Heather Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXAR2awDwwg40UXDk37cVoc0wbldzi0KXyWx4JXALGtSKDUndD1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The food was good but this is a very NOISY restaurant on the small side with reflective walls and floors. There was a table full of very loud family members and friends of the owner that made it impossible to hear people sitting at your own table. Several customers left because of the noise. Instead of addressing the issue, the owner laughed it off (favoring his friends and family above customers) stating "they're from East Van". I thought he would knock off the price of an entree because of the noise but it was full fare. I would't recommend dining in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Thomas Tricarico","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhws5bVYDwmrI4nzI8NtjFY5tCFNmhM_PZ57tj9M9bdO7Dag=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a Great dinner last night at That Table..a real family based restaurant with great, friendly, accommodating service and the food was very good. The porrions were generous and very tasty. The Alfredo was not quite to my wife's liking but they immediately made it right to her liking and it turned out great. My Spaghetti Amalfi was excellent. We had a great Sangria too. The best..was their cannoli for dessert.  They were The Best cannolis we have ever had in Vancouver..home made..and we told them so. We will be back..and you should give them a try. Thanks for an enjoyable evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOWZ5ULwwW8hMgXeHSDkXmGLNmZEyZJKNch3euT&fid=0x0:0xf2949084e08f7717"],"When":"2021-11-5"}]

Another order was French toast which tasted just like toast and bacon which was over cooked and burned. There was no refill on coffee because she never went around. The order cost us over $50. We should have gone to another restaurant.
I‚Äôm just sharing how we felt. Maybe we just ordered wrong. Now we know NOT to go back again. Sorry.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeTp5XuKH0_Uf6BP_Z559hhKuO9HLsJn6W4Zp2&fid=0x0:0xe9900134f02548b5"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Nathan Woods","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYlKwIGO9PHjqLgc7mRGN7qYIzJ_Yb1JOij4343pL12ye4fG4D-w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Everybody reviewing this place like it's a five star restaurant.

[{"Name":"Kimberly W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyEcFWm9KlF1A5qUr48_2k5NqNkBKB28_JBHp8Hk3SydvKzo4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven‚Äôt had authentic Singaporean cuisine but I‚Äôve heard good things about Singapore hawker so I finally decided to try. The staff seemed very friendly right upon entering. We ordered the pork belly, beef skewers, and the Nasi Goreng. Everything was very tasty, the Nasi Goreng had still a kick to it despite asking for mild. My complain was that the shrimp chips were a bit stale. The beef skewers were kind of on the skinnier side, but were definitely not dry and the peanut sauce was amazing. The crispy pork belly was probably what shined the most. I‚Äôm not a huge pork belly fan but this pork belly was not too fatty, extremely moist and tasty. We even got a free dessert at the end which was a pleasant surprise, and it was a delicious way to cleanse your palate after meat/spice. I can‚Äôt speak for how authentic the food is but overall we really enjoyed this place and would come again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9JNMLelRiisg_saezjbRCw_pidLJCdc5JZuAB&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-10-23"},{"Name":"Junyong Hong (Junny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI68GoItOKY8hE2VMit7EfVOjKre8YhHLAJmsrHl632hIf8sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You get big portions of tasty food for decent price. Staffs were friendly and the restaurant was clean. This is our second time coming and we will come back again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOyyfJHeAIV46RNOEis4Klz8lkAy-V4zNstd2SJ&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-12-14"},{"Name":"Jack Pajak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7kRSq5QM1wGXm36_dbE9YR6CpcUs9VUAhu1SxvpJkrQ-nGO0N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time trying Singapore Hawker and I have to say that I am impressed! Our food was absolutely delicious, with great portions. I highly recommend the Roti Canai and the Mee Goreng. Great for families and kids. Service here is friendly and our food came out fast! Definitely worth a visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPACVFg29cV1QEgOLsn1pyLN7LDEZluy1PFmiTk&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Marilyn Mok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUikqrTCDS8NJxP3Hkk4jQDiHEi8RL4gQluQjwU1f2e462S8t3D=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First off, I wasn't impressed with the atmosphere. The place looks more like a staff canteen than a cafe.

I ordered the Char Kuay Teow and my friend ordered the fried nonya eggplant.  The Char Kuay Teow had a nice wok flavor but is not as sweet and flavorful as I like. It was fried with only the flat white rice noodle and missing the yellow noodle. The fish cake used did not have the springy texture that is found in Singapore fishballs and fish cake. There's also not enough egg in it. The nonya eggplant was nicely fried but I'm not sure where the nonya reference came in. I was also very disappointed that they do not have Singapore style kopi or teh.

The plus point was that the service staff was nice and friendly. And they offered a free small bowl of burbur chacha for dessert.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPqSwNclcQGOBN5-0DD5v221mnMrRsKq067l4xK&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"grace","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXclLzFOZebBq0D1P6DXbTNuAdCFzeYlMZFVvgi1A5VbWvym50Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"food: really delicious and flavorful. the Singaporean laksa is soo creamy and rich, and the fried squid is super crispy and crunchy

service: the service was okay, but they don't take your orders for food. so you have to either go up to the cashier, or scan the QR code on the table to order.

atmosphere: I really like the atmosphere of this restaurant. it's modern, clean, and simple. there's also a really cool wall with the skyline of Singapore and some famous architecture on it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMypF7B-MThYJHZbwWgKhQ5Kjm7zoNR7XF3LFz0&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"carol liem","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUCuYohzwvL-I_7dNVbbjdcGA122HF_X2tQ1V3VyXmvEJB9WWU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We had authentic Singapore food here. My son liked the Hainanese Chicken Rice. I liked the satays and Sayur Lodeh. We will visit this restaurant whenever we miss Singaporean food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNp0oaI4IOKuEtfewT6MXGHW7pSWDfgMC-pKZ9-&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-7-16"},{"Name":"Irene Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLx3-d7cbUWi2OAKcOP1RtCCE35UuLboYj6B1-X-4h1WkqA8nN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The naan was delicious too. I went with my parents. This is not a restaurant where the waiters necessary wait on your table all the time since you order at the counter and pay upfront; regardless, the delicious food is totally worth it and eating the leftovers the next day was even better.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM5DPjWLhIpFJ3nHNkI3EOtYaVqI8N3PM6TcSBe&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Agni K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkDG9ralu9RS3nZ0v4vIcP6bNgjmOEKH-8N8DikYFi0AF_Esan=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is by far the best Singaporean food I‚Äôve had. Ever. The flavours are out of this world! They are very reasonably priced and portions are substantial. This was our second visit, after discovering this place almost 2 years ago by chance. We remember being absolutely blown away by the flavours and freshness of the food the first time and it didn‚Äôt disappoint this time around. Talk about consistency, they delivered the same marvel of aromas and decadence with every dish. Even if you don‚Äôt live in burnaby, this place is absolutely worth a drive!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNINDn-QcLHPxQYtnDxg2SfW63uyQsm22zdLQwh&fid=0x0:0xbc7025c18f4ae0f7"],"When":"2024-5-6"}]

[{"Name":"Kaylee Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrnelwesLWszVvjanLNlsfSIxKVIQPnh9SEyYTfIQJ3XkS9yt8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A great Italian spot near Como Lake area! The pizza with its thin crust and fresh ingredients is fantastic‚Äîdefinitely the best I've found within a 15-20 minute drive from Surrey. The carbonara is okay, but I'm hoping to try a better pasta option in their menu. The service is always friendly and welcoming. I visit almost every month for the excellent pizza and warm atmosphere!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEuS0Mu6EwQyj-eOwZklsK5XdyKwUeWnRSKQ5P&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-11-5"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"If you‚Äôre craving authentic Italian cuisine, The Golden Boot in Coquitlam is a must-visit. We recently dined there and had the Ferrari Pizza and the Funghi Pasta, and both dishes exceeded our expectations.

The Ferrari Pizza was a masterpiece of fresh ingredients and perfect execution. The thin, crispy crust paired beautifully with its rich toppings, striking the perfect balance between flavor and texture. It was clear that great care and quality ingredients went into every bite.

The Funghi Pasta was equally outstanding. The earthy richness of the mushrooms combined with a creamy sauce created a dish that was both comforting and indulgent. The pasta was perfectly cooked, and the flavors were well-balanced, making it one of the best pasta dishes we‚Äôve had in a long time.

The Golden Boot offers more than just great food; it provides an inviting and cozy atmosphere that enhances the dining experience. The staff were warm, attentive, and knowledgeable, making our evening even more enjoyable.

If you‚Äôre looking for a fresh and authentic Italian experience in Coquitlam, The Golden Boot is a gem worth discovering. We can‚Äôt wait to return and explore more of their menu!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNBr1HapyFm5MQNZ6xipl9yNR8QHro3gqqHsWMA&fid=0x0:0xec9b84a60327fe07"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Jamie K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbJ2U1LY4qMlQOmrUVddM2YAaHlcLuD0VLF8l26mbYtDI6YXU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was good especially pizza was delicious. Overall, we were really let down by the food quality, service, and value for money. The service was friendly and quick, even though the restaurant was quite busy. The cozy and casual atmosphere made it a great place to enjoy a relaxed meal with friends.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpsq4YTu4ivkuGsCDt4D3kpUni4tLXnJJTZDv6&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-12-10"},{"Name":"Tim Cho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlAeRGbdix5pzSJ294H4Xr78Nd64DzEa5cdHefPrVDxRdp4rOfSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an incredible dining experience at Jimoco! Loved everything from service, decor, and atmosphere to the food üòç
Portions were reasonable as well as the price, especially their lunch menu! Each dish was flavorful and was not overpowering or over salty.
I felt welcomed and at east with their friendly and genuine service and attitude.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNpkF0_ft2xTh9nJfLPKphM7a228eRGRU-qC_s4&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Michael Fierro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGxPiXz4VjAC2xy7rVHkMhqRHuzRHqAbOMz5r7KH0luLvvpF8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment I stepped into this restaurant every detail‚Äîfrom the ambient lighting to the attentive service‚Äîset the stage for a meal I‚Äôll be dreaming about for years.

I started with the truffle fries. Oh. My. Goodness. These weren‚Äôt just fries‚Äîthey were a transcendental experience. Golden, crispy, and kissed by the divine essence of truffle oil, they practically melted in my mouth. Each fry was a little piece of heaven, perfectly seasoned and dangerously addictive.

Then came the seafood risotto, and let me tell you, it was nothing short of perfection. Each grain of rice was tender, infused with a rich, oceanic symphony of flavors. The seafood? Plump, fresh, and cooked to absolute perfection‚Äîlike it had been caught that very morning. Every bite was a revelation, a crescendo of tastes that danced on my palate.

And then came the pi√®ce de r√©sistance: the blueberry cheesecake. If angels bake, this is what their desserts taste like. The cheesecake was impossibly creamy, with a luscious texture that felt like silk on my tongue. The blueberries, bursting with freshness, added a vibrant sweetness that complemented the tangy richness of the cake. It wasn‚Äôt just a dessert‚Äîit was a masterpiece.

I can‚Äôt recommend this restaurant enough. Every dish was a love letter to flavor, every bite a testament to culinary brilliance. If you haven‚Äôt been yet, drop everything and go‚Äîyou‚Äôre in for the meal of a lifetime!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM58BQjrKJtJ5ufQrfKYQ6aYKuCmRpHzR64I1YM&fid=0x0:0x7c8e5688b857cfe7"],"When":"2024-11-17"},{"Name":"Serena Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9dCXJiXkT2Yw03SJdaNBPt4M_g0YqE6WK4iltbPxjJjyx6Z3vBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A cozy, peaceful restaurant with a lovely atmosphere! [{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Pe√±a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We finally discovered the best KBBQ in Coquitlam at Galbi! After trying several spots, this is the only place that truly got my partner excited about KBBQ. What sets Galbi apart is their focus on the quality of the meat rather than just the side dishes‚Äîa huge plus in our book.

They handled our reservation quickly, and we were fortunate to snag a table before it got really busy. While the space is a bit cozy, the meal was absolutely fantastic. The marinated beef short ribs were so irresistible that we ended up ordering extra.

We were expecting the bill to be around $200, but were pleasantly surprised when it came out $60 cheaper‚Äîeven with the tip included. I‚Äôm definitely bringing my friends here next time. Can‚Äôt wait to come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtXU7g1Mdshu7JLv6kgKpUYZu5LSk1yfwe--bA&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Suzanne Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA92S6YKukSMnbRa5H7tG8jeNNTYeIVRPnSfmNiCXXXyAauEzN0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came here on a Thursday evening and thankfully we came early! The place filled up pretty quickly around 7pm. We ordered the fresh beef ribs, pork jowl, and pork belly with skin on (thick cut). Prices are reasonable for the quality of meat and quantity (each portion is by weight). I found the soybean paste soup very salty, but once diluted it was quite tasty! Enjoyed the salad and sides, but they charge for extra side dishes and restrict you to 3 pieces of romaine lettuce per meat order (which seems a bit stingy for a small side item). There was also dirt on the lettuce, which they washed off and returned to us... Rice is ordered on the side for $2 each.

Overall a clean storefront with friendly staff, fresh quality ingredients, and a fun no-frills kbbq experience! We spent around $100 for 3 people.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMolYBIiES1jj5IW8KrAnPCgFR-qT5oYoTiMa20&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-11-3"},{"Name":"MAY Îß§Ïù¥ Elford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxJVIiA7BVVmzUGqT6sRzP7-hCdYJttIOnYMeIvWOWZPmq7cr7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A Saturday evening out with my friends. 4 of us ended up at Galbi. We ordered the pork belly with skin on, Galbi, and the cold noodle. Everything was delicious‚Ä¶ the bean paste soup was so yummy.
They gave us side dishes, but to add more, there is an extra fee.
Service was great and there have a lot of parking. Definitely worth going!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOiNt4K-oH50HrFkg3LuUdGSxwY6y2kJMYXzNyD&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-4-28"},{"Name":"Ananda Enkhtur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkkmVVa6j0bCuttopPInRikVrpr7LXYSHoZtWk3dhng__J_lZi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Tried this place the other day and it was pretty good! Not many items on the menu that you can choose from but overall the taste was delicious. Especially the red bean soup and the corn cheese was so good. Like many Korean restaurants there are variety of side dishes that come with the meal and the portions for each one was generous too! Would recommend to come as a big group tho!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJ-sZtMzSf8pafLObOPwMYuYYoPalr6VIO6Vud&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-2-20"},{"Name":"Nat A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWnjKr4KNFAObzj2bIvH9BRInxwKsSvEg1PM25bKfvhxtWZTWHoog=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Tried this place out for the first time. We had the marinated beef and pork short ribs. The beef was tasty but the pork was just okay. I had a few pieces of the beef that were hard and fatty. The portion size for the meat was average. The soup appetizer, kimchi, and pickled raddish were good. They provided a pitcher of water, no complimentary tea offered.

The selection on the menu is minimal.

Service was average. We had to wave over to the waiters every time we needed something. They did not come up to us and ask how things were after they gave us our food.

Overall, the food was decent but I wouldn't come back when there are other Korean BBQ restaurants with more selection.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPb8x1RQYXa6xENsHZCT5yvKAqEx9VI05wYGrBK&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2022-12-11"},{"Name":"Molly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLxkBBeHfwDYZEHKteGzubNOwVdGJVg2Kn4pysUcR2QBA2w0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jessi was my server tonight she was very friendly and attentive. 5 stars for my experience. Food was great. The free soup was so good I purchased another one! They didn't seem to have the salt soya sauce dip tray that you get in other places. Maybe you have to ask for it? I don't care for it I don't add extra stuff to my meat. I got the short ribs and the prime beef so good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVumoVlQ2Nr7knqW9lb01ghVZite-FLKkjhE2dVSofQsuYeSfVW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Galbi is my best place for Korean BBQ in Vancouver. The meats were fresh, tender and nicely marbled also marinated short ribs were well seasoned. Excellent service and reasonable price. I usually visit 1-2times a week. Try this place if you are meat lover!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO4RXzzsu5isoPwissTXgbEx26fjigui8uk6uai&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2023-2-28"},{"Name":"Hwa D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwQyjGi41SNIX6tVkw-8BfQdSHpbL_wDTFcZShwlM2dHZ3e1AW_w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited this restaurant and was thoroughly impressed. The marinated beef short ribs were absolutely delicious.
What made the experience even more enjoyable was the exceptional service. The staff were incredibly friendly and attentive, ensuring that our dining experience was delightful from start to finish. I highly recommend this restaurant","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOklX-zzm88iNsKQfia31-tC_DHWRFqVfVdVqKY&fid=0x0:0x3acdae584ead321a"],"When":"2024-3-17"}]

[{"Name":"Deidrea Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUutwpTcfZUKTs5jf7YxXXOoISr_9o8CMM9MqyCNl6Ehvh_tbyG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ordered the gangster pizza last night, when it arrived it was hot and looked amazing!!! Fresh ingredients and tasted so good! I definitely recommend ordering from here... it's a little more expensive but worth it in my opinion. I'm also posting so more pictures cause last night me and my son decided to try their new pizza called the SAUSAGE MUSHROOM MAGIC PIZZA and people out there I can't stress how amazing this pizza was!!!! If you love mushrooms and sausage on your pizza this is for you... its packed full of fresh toppings, cooked to perfection and so yummy! Great pizza worth every penny.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMNBsirUsZVNr_npyUgVymemdPtze20Mup9eQnv&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2024-4-6"},{"Name":"Kwang s Koo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFo3VGQh4dEQHrPSivYNI5XIEy1BykoaCVmEDpxsBAeHTAFA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoy the food took advantage of happy hour. Pizzas are always good.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkNHdvEo9jI-nay4UU6CpxMLTKG6MVgleq0gZy&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Cheryl A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocId3JTMrjtqtdmj_0XOBMchbLGhcrTAO0uBPM1jzlHcNAjL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"No where does it post that the salad comes with  bread crotons - I would have thought being that we ordered glutton free crust they would have asked about it when  ordering our salad - next time I‚Äôll be sure to tell them . Our waitress was painfully slow - perhaps she was new - but I think there should have been some experienced servers  guiding her?  It was not very busy there -","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOYOBxXrSjzg_YcoiXaS-7Ry9RGlb7Hpk1fZtE&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2024-5-2"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mean Ed's Pizza on Austin Street in Coquitlam is a neighborood syaple. We ordered the Godfather Which is pepperoni and tomato pizza, with different types of cheese which was flavorful and satisfying. However, my kids opted for the herb and garlic oil pizza, which unfortunately was quite dry. If you're considering the garlic and oil option, I'd recommend ordering it with marinara sauce to add some much-needed moisture and flavor. Overall, Good experience the staff is friendly and ambiance was nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7JBRA_74hqBnICEIXhIIHy57WIC-163xRpLQv&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2024-6-1"},{"Name":"Sean Bartlette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLt6yELNcyy9z0uDF0-vlqNgSGzW8ZS_cZzfxnuFF3pI46v3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I cannot for the life of me understand the positive reviews of this chain.  Their whole thing seems to be lots of low quality toppings, with minimal sauce and cheese.  The crust is a cracker, not even flat bread.  I get if you want to fill up on the toppings and not bread, but $40 for a large of this quality is a bad deal.  The service was great, prompt and attentive, nice location.  The food is a reflection of the chain, not this location.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joshua (ThickBurger_Bites)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbIhhMlbxk7OIMpcaP-aSx2m75kt8-mqmXoXAJQ5K99gnxiff1zg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great food. Great service. Great location for a quick bite or gatherings.

We had the large gangster pizza and hot wings. Pizza was delicious, well made and didn‚Äôt leave a greasy taste in your mouth. Hot wings weren‚Äôt hot per-se, barely a kick, but paired with the ranch dip, a must try.

We paid about 60 for the large pizza, wings as well as fountain drinks.

Service was amazing, one server on shift but super attentive and our cups never ran empty.

Would recommend visiting this place with friends and family, or even a date too. Place was relatively quiet with ample tables available on a tuesday evening.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO2d_rsmzyEmHTxa1fMiRvVikIueFIK6Fy_nZJu&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2023-2-1"},{"Name":"omid piruzan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIo1fwmgnihU89y2BheYltZR5Di8RxdgtYiIoXg3sm1NX9OE88=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very Cozy and classic interior, takes you back to 80ies. Very friendly staff, clean and organized shop. We ordered Combo medium size, good for 3 persons. A bit smaller than average pizza standards. If you are 4 big guys probably need at least 2 large size pizzas.
We visit once a year for school fundraiser night.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMTCYWh8BgvpO7pW648FzzDQdHfnhS945AkONcr&fid=0x0:0xeeb96139e4be3af4"],"When":"2022-2-23"},{"Name":"Fhm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfpRdgpo_biUMzsiu-CrM0VVbN_mhJeWqgoaHeNPFxNiHSrqE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The crust is perfectly crispy, the toppings are fresh and delicious, and the service is always friendly.
Pro tip: try the Godfather and Meat Lovers pizzas - they're absolutely mouthwatering!" üçï","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Herman Ma","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNkiZiWTHH4AMcQS5P0e7HeuuBX0dNeXwCFqQ9w2c9ob5i37E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had family dinner here and I will definitely be back.  Food was very flavorful, portion sizes were good, and food came out quickly.  The servers gave food recommendations for dishes to try and the price was very fair.  I think they have dim sum during the day as well so will have to try that next time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMonnMwhCPQ5-XwzFWgPNiomd-FGpNlwc-t7bnd&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Nathan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6aOctokU9KmE5fwo6-6THfOky0imQyJSKP9b0jCAM3iXNSZtK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Service has rapidly gone downhill over the years. We used to be regular customers here but found the owner becoming stingy and greedy. Gradually, prices got higher while the food portions got smaller (not enough broth in our takeout photo).

They also must have changed chefs, because the food isn‚Äôt the same. Noodles are often soggy, and the flavour is bland. I wonder if it‚Äôs because they‚Äôre trying to be cheap and not be generous with the sauce/portion in an attempt to save money.

Too bad. 1/5 stars due to bad service and low quality.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPjlS7Oxzhu2MyzUILv0QT8d_Z0I0FX_Amdwp7Z&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Ryan Gardner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITFVXg73_7U2jrgVJP956L7ME6PdIgxrIx7_Y2WNfstwovYQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Our server Acknowledged that the chicken was raw in our "almond chicken", asked if we wanted to have it made fresh. We declined after losing our appetite eating half of it already. Charged us full price and refused to discount it or take it off the bill.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM9onc9XoaKGsH0gx-OZqBjqtK1odNMtkaRpz9B&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-7-28"},{"Name":"G W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVG1FFo9GTnRGQNpjln74dhjBn3V4nGRQE_Yjur_OV6HYJsv04F_g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow. Authentic Chinese cuisine. The Asian community was mostly the customers, telling me it's very good food because of the amount of customers here. The food was delicious. I am pescatarian and I ordered veg soya chow mein, garlic broccoli and  prawns and veggies. incredible flavour and portions. ordered three for two of us and took half home.
Service was right away taking care of you as you come thru the door. Greeted with a smile. Average is $20 per item but it's a fair amount served.
Simple open area with chairs and tables. Clean and Simple
Definitely recommend if your looking for a lovely Chinese dinner. They also deliver. Deliveries were flying out the door.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPUF5yRtUBjPGFCnYBY-h3xLv6R_D-g4cpbxSG5&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-5-20"},{"Name":"niya won","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKmwV9ujHyf266hG5NTci1Gc0JLSXKmgPbP7vaySC8bLv6tjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"As a delivery driver, I often pick up orders from this restaurant. On several occasions, I needed to use the restroom during my work, but my request was denied. This not only caused inconvenience for me but could also lead to delays in delivering food to customers, as drivers are forced to find alternative facilities. I hope the restaurant can understand the challenges delivery drivers face and consider offering basic amenities. Supporting drivers in this way would benefit both the drivers and the customers who rely on timely deliveries.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Harrison Ens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXy6nnUCtAVE291ykxHAR5AkhEKCNqUnONOVioWeL9fWaUVxpaY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Squid Congee had wonderful taste & portion size. The lady taking my money berated me for not tipping & a $1.25 card fee for under $50 purchases  is ludicrous.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQTrkcUwPdFIpt-zTJV97ME6qSP-5z0jaCjoWK&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2024-8-29"},{"Name":"Chanelle D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCEGtGi_rnAXcez2UGfi8tPvkrtnC3uoCyaDz_NpX-tJAfWp2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This was a restaurant choice of my mom for her special day. For a new Chinese restaurant in the neighbourhood, we expected a much higher caliber of service. We were seated immediately because we made a reservation for about 10 people. We were quite disappointed by the service. We ordered several dishes to start but the dishes were served one at a time with 10 minutes in between. It was ridiculous! We ended up with one dish on the lazy susan making its rounds between 10 people for about 10 minutes before the next one was brought out.. then another dish. 10 minutes later, another dish. It was a painful and unbelievably slow service. Finally they brought out the main entrees after 45 minutes later. The restaurant was not at full capacity but we are guessing that the staff do not have a proper workflow. The dishes were OK. I would never recommend this place to anyone who wants good, reliable service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9nJ3DkW9F_LztkgcSm-Twy_-c2QvegygKatD9&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2019-5-13"},{"Name":"Henry Liu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpG2mtSpUTo0L511zE_jfvNAiacFxGCQ9_Rt-Bqodv9L-Kg21JLA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Foods are good and delicious. Price are reasonable. Service good and courteous. The only funny point is when order food with free drinks, drinks cannot come latter.  The boss said they are too busy, if drinks come later, we have to pay extra as regular price. *This never heard or happened in any restaurants that I had visited* As a whole, the restaurant is worth to visit again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQYbpq-CENX8zXL4Nyki8rNXq1d94Bfwg4m8iy&fid=0x0:0x6d2dd5cf087247d2"],"When":"2021-11-21"}]

[{"Name":"Anne Champagne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbHErxHCaeTkPt_idxR9bzDUUa0MUdm576VB9GtGX0Q8Rf-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place was a great surprise as I have not been to a Browns in years and I had previously been very disappointed with their prices and menu. However, after stopping at Cactus Club and seeing their selections and prices ($42 for a bottle of house wine!!!! that was not really very good at all), my bestie and I grabbed our coats and drove 4 min farther to Browns Social House.  We were  looking for a hostess to see if we were to seat ourselves when this pleasant young man with a huge friendly smile came up and asked if we needed help.  (I assumed he was a server.) He said we could sit where we wanted and we  chose a nice corner table and sat down. We laughed and told the waitress about our day. (Another whole story). Needless to say, the wine was very good and reasonably priced, the food was tasty and served quickly and the young man who had seated us came over and was actually the manager!   Our server had told him of our ridiculous day and he actually came and talked to us and thoroughly added positivity to our evening of a very long and crazy day. Carter is excellent at his job and our server said they all think he's just the best. So I stand corrected on my previous thoughts of Browns.  Carter and his staff changed my mind completely and instead of going to Cactus Club I will most definitely stop here instead. And currently, their Happy hour menu has changed and is now half price wine from 3-5 every day!  We will try that next time for sure!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janice Chau","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVuB0K-5M1meSEpaNhkSCxzMPwN-1TgA7zbcO9oRfCt3rzUnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I liked the ambiance. Big screen showing hockey for NHL fans wanting to catch the game. Service was good, we were a group of 8 and they were fuss-free about separate cheques for everyone and didn't impose an automatic service fee. (Tip options did begin at 18% however).

Single occupant bathrooms were a big plus.

The food itself left something to be desired - I got the crusted cod with rice and salad. Not bad but also not something you would come here for. I find the menu lacking compared to other similar restaurants.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNAeTDmeVnEoxDZSg953Z9xcM06v1sIPCHdsVXd&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2024-2-11"},{"Name":"Natalya","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8u2LiiW4DqYRUnIjENKyngvDjgwKhrJfLcThqD75I390F36fkdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My first impression of the place went to hell ... As we were being seated, the so-called waitress that seated us had absolutely  no equitte or professionalism .... when asked nicely to clean the table as it had food on  it, she decided to flick it off with her finger  landing onto my  chair...ü§Æ
Informing  the manager she did clean table  however  thought it was funny experience üôÑ
After witnessing that, it turned me off whole place.. I decided not to eat  while my acquaintance  did ......
Overall, ok place physically  but wouldn't  go in ther  again. It lacks  professionalism and cleanness, it seems ......","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPdpewnauFKLOAm8rJNV9MzErQ72oDvzOCaNPgC&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2023-4-10"},{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good-looking restaurant, great atmosphere. Good service and menu selection. Crusted cod was perfectly cooked but the rice was so plain.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM6YLf1a-nb1X9HVqRR-VqUSax6pDES_KZ4D10l&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2024-7-25"},{"Name":"Leslie F.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBWZ72oe3Fj3q6Ev_Yexva_R2RIuoAsXhINuQFz6i-KsTDhf4q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love this location!! Jasmine was our server and she gave us amazing service.  The Calamari was a great choice as an appetizer.  The Dragon Bowl with chicken was amazing, which I highly recommend.  The Chicken Sandwich and Fries are great too.  Very nice modern, clean washrooms that are single and private and or wheelchair accessible if you require.  Order in or take out! Lots of options to choose from.  Beautiful patio seat available here as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqa_AhITyiOLmDOxXw76yu9o3n80-9K3iEMCSs&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2022-9-6"},{"Name":"Ben Overbiƒá","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoVhGHglJdtYYOjPnpE4XuCKcPR_fHkA81yjnGNrvUZ8sopcLi=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Not bad casual bar food or dining. Nothing to die for but nothing to really complain about it‚Äôs pretty safe to choose browns as an option for a quick bite.
Steaks better than cactus but not as good as joeys. Mini nachos taste better and are more fresh than the loaded nachos.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbGm0PGZyx2ZRcwKAHVryNjpkQk0tgiJDDNvvq&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2023-7-16"},{"Name":"Grimoaldo Assuncao","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXU2Y0QnGVfV3sT7avvzv_BELncEzuG0SSyXqGRkB5XwNyC_gPK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is an amazing restaurant to visit.

Delicious food, drinks and deserts.

If you are planning to have a happy hour, to celebrate a party or have an special moment with your partner or family, do not hesitate to visit this place.

Also very attentive staff.

With individual man‚Äôs and woman‚Äôs washrooms.

A great ambient and environment.

I really recommend it.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPOQK2alQIPSPLVXfmzm7rp7--PM2TF2CEK2Z2t&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2022-11-20"},{"Name":"Sandhya Iyengar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWYcFo4p7ZievJafEzdENBwKuQ3ZO3m9AoFLaWoaCRR85W5BSKlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"2nd visit: This time we came for early dinner. We ordered beer with nachos (not loaded) asked for nachos and informed to give guacamole on the side. They did get our order as asked. Really appreciate their service. Then ordered chicken quesadilla and southwest veggie bowl. Last but not least tried their carrot cake. I must say one of the best cakes I have had. However, the cream on top was not required, as the cake itself is very delicious and heavy. A must try carrot cake. Would come again.
‚Äê-------------------------------------------------------------------------
We came here for lunch. First dine in experience. We loved the food, ambience and service. We ordered Avocado toast with poarched eggs and southwest brunch bowl. The food was tasty and delicious. The fresh orange juice was also very tasty.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNccAq_MCRWV4J-P2wCfOBAtwOoAk-tMd86BwjN&fid=0x0:0x6b7be498f395cd22"],"When":"2022-6-27"}]

[{"Name":"Andy Leung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBfPzDHg9RmwaF6xT8BiwrCt06LiR0mWps8IZZP7KGtsdBbQne=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stepped into the restaurant not really looking to eat but found the place open amongst many closed restaurants. Staff greeted me at the door and I asked for a menu which was promptly provided. A staff member (tall young man with perm) provided a thorough explanation of the menu and what different food options was available and the restaurant was about. I opted to dine in after the thorough explanation and genuine service even before I sat. Once I settled on an order the staff loudly shouted to the kitchen staff and proceeded to hand me utensils/water. Moments later I could hear a meat mallet being slammed against what can be presumed to be my order (pork loin cutlet). Not long after I sat down another customer came in asking to look at the menu and explaining they're unfamiliar with the concept. the food came out quickly. The deep fried loin was pleasantly plated; light tasting; and juicy with flavour. 5/5 food. 5/5 service. 5/5 ambiance. Seems like cabbage salad sides are unlimited too! Beginning to end this was 5/5. Came on Tuesday Oct 22nd 3:30pm. Katsuya - Coquitlam if you're reading this please recognize your staff for such outstanding service and delicious food!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMqilRDdGE6NydQWz1wbHRJAZ10XC-zTFgOgoJS&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Kristine Aizle Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYbQRMW0sa4F7v9y0xsCWOZxC721h53-90ZVy0Q0mpX6y_Og=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We are greeted by all staff as soon we entered the place and got seated right away. We ordered the special set and it did not disappoint (the katsu is crispy and not greasy üòã). The set was large portion and we end up taking the leftovers to go. Good place to eat variety of katsu. Will come back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOY-fx02u_VLQCLdpnDytZZVO7vSsU3Eniy5syQ&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Jack Bi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZ4Bsv7wnjfj756aRVvVyi5fPfQhBIMCe6kqNdp4pTbIyytg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the pleasure of trying katsu in Burquitlam recently, and I really appreciated the wonderful service. The food was delicious, and it was lovely to have both a salad and a refill of rice included‚Äîsuch a thoughtful addition! That said, I did notice the music was a bit on the loud side, which made it a little hard to fully enjoy the experience. Overall, though, it was a nice outing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGrjvypMFCi2IrGkRiEDeUZr2eyCD4xHboYTPz&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"TS OS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIrxJ8Fjd3bGSI8mWbF186RbFWyg_DW73VTS3OIkFaxPfXFBEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"DonKatsu was pretty good. Pricing is up there with its competitors. Quality of food is comparable too but cabbage salad and rice refills don‚Äôt seem to exist at this place at free of charge. We also really liked the pasta, which was surprisingly tasty especially the sauce. Place usually isn‚Äôt packed so you should be able to get seated fairly shortly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOJbZSl1M1e8lL8ztqGh1BRqzbPMALyWsOjK81b&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Ben","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLUPgdSyWZ3aTWwwnESZaSRJf8t_y_oBRQlEfjK-SB4dJfKj64=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Katsu sauce had a unique taste, but overall it was the best tonkatsu place I've had in Vancouver. The taste was great, and the portion size was very enough for the price, which made it very satisfying. The restaurant had a small number of tables compared to the size of the space, which made it comfortable and pleasant. The staff's service was also excellent.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPtnMx8MZVn9g_Opb-r96C0P49aZ1kpq0KR6bq2&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-29"},{"Name":"Karen Abary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuR4UCsHnAPqLBeNDszrqXOmjrbOmLQnn5L3CErUSQyQJWrM8qqw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you‚Äôre cruising through North Road and craving something beyond the usual Korean fare, Katsuya is where you need to be! üòã This place has all the mouthwatering options‚Äîfrom rich, savory udon to crispy, golden katsu. üçõ And when I say the portions are huge, I mean HUGE! üôå

I went for the Katsu Set, and it was an absolute game-changer. The katsu was perfectly crispy on the outside, tender on the inside, paired with a warm, flavorful bowl of udon, plus a variety of side dishes that kept me coming back for more. üçúüç§ Every bite was better than the last!

But what really made the experience unforgettable? The service! üôè The staff is so friendly, super accommodating, and genuinely makes you feel like you‚Äôre right at home. üíñ And the best part? The prices are totally worth it for the big portions and top-notch food you get.

Katsuya is definitely a new favorite, and I‚Äôll be back for sure! ü•≥ So if you‚Äôre after a cozy, flavorful meal that‚Äôll leave you stuffed and satisfied, this spot is a must-try! #KatsuyaCravings #FoodieHeaven #NorthRoadEats #WorthEveryBite","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNI92G2XWHYPDUt7OD1zn2lu0xp98OwnV25kSEQ&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"Cyril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWK-_ySZg3bQEFmes-BY-8D2FucE-bUlde_oHJOB4IAApjGcLEN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came on a date with my girlfriend, we were greeted as we stepped into the place and were seated right away, love the atmosphere lovely music that fits the season and also love the bread displays it shows that the breading is authentic. I was overwhelmed in a way in which the food had a excellent presentation and the portions were worth the pricing, also love the sesame seeds which you can grind by yourself it gives it a nice detail to add to the meal. Most importantly the Katsu is cooked just right, my girlfriend got the silver cheese katsu and the cheese was just right melting and not too hot, recommend this place for real, nice little hidden spot for a date or for a filling meal :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUvIHVBWOi-4eHV9Ift76vddqGCB1k7bOIVPwn&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Anish Banik Arko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWI0KM6WKbnZVsLpZ9NMfdm_mhCSCv9FEUTS0DOwOV0D99wyYin4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food has always been amazing here. Have been coming here for a long time. Their special set katsu menu comes with enough food for two and the variety of foods really adds to the dining experience. The presentation is also on point. Would highly recommend to try out their red carbonara katsu with your choice of protein.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaP-aKaqJ3ToDeKrzL9oDtvbRVJxEmm8p4ZWAp&fid=0x0:0xc180c2232f3f7e85"],"When":"2024-7-23"}]

[{"Name":"Diane (Dineoutwithdee)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJfHVJSjIKAcPEXNIfUcWAtOeYHaXavqJYPtVJZ3lhCbCbpeo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a great place to get authentic Greek food at reasonable prices. Great value here and delicious food, too! The place is busy so best to come early to grab a seat. I recommend the lamb shoulder, calamari and the chicken & beef souvlaki!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP42asUKI5KLp9y9RM9Fit82mrJ9Qd6-ziYb3Sh&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Emily Lu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEvwebxzOOvHfn2UnHwr4i_lsQ_4WBBcdmwEUmGOtZoyfwO9Mg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good food and great flavour! The pita bread is probably the best in the lower mainland! The portion is also generous. We took the dinner home and that was a whole other meal in and out of itself.
The place is quite bit but it gets 80% full and becomes busy even at 4:30 pm! The space between tables is small so I had to move my chains/out of the way for people/waiters to pass through all the time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_rakdPK5k-z808EXZ_h6jLZlPrNWM6u9uhOQY&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-10-7"},{"Name":"duane r neufeld","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhhlb1lcJQnDlyAPy1R2d_GOddZm-jMhyJJsiO9YhD02HRj38=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow these folks have it dialed in!!! Do not come here unless you have a LARGE appetite.  Monster serving size and you will love eating it all to the last morsel.  Every aspect of the food is perfect.  Come with your friend with a large appetite.  They will not be disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDW_s96eeWP-6cW7H05QxCPA7hObO2L0nmcgN1&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-12-22"},{"Name":"Justine H (Sunny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmvMXm-P_-zaDju2DtLb4mJNuo8OiXNtbw6zPhVOcICWtiAOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place! We ordered the calamari from their dinner menu and their souvlaki. Their calamari was very fresh and crunchy. Their meat was a little hard but you're able to request if you prefer it to be well done, medium rare, etc.

The restaurant is much cleaner than other Greek restaurants we have been to and their prices are standard so we probably keep coming back time to time. :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP9BOPAe0Tu_IZ0MhDzHLYvccA1b9J6cef-PjwK&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-7-7"},{"Name":"Bella Mills","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9Ii_MUe1yBHkf4i7hAtgKoYsTZWvSgOMwOkR9qA3QXh9dyYpPrg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are here at 4:00 pm on Saturday and luck to have table without making reservation.
Food and service are great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNyHTwJlp2n1QQowmTTyN0vMGdc4AOtJgiUnj4G&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Kate Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIjE4MSAa0c4Uqc8iOt1LfqIkJDL1ULa2Z17gRh4YDWMExQ1A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Good thing I made a reservation cuz wow it was so full on a weekday night. They try to squeeze as many tables in there and my seat bumps into the person behind me. Parking is limited to a few in front and a few on the sides.

We quickly got seated and ordered our meals. Everything was enormous. The mostly I've seen at any greek restaurant. Definitely worth the price.

Calamari was standard. I would have liked it with some seasoning.

The lamb chops were fantastic! I asked for medium rare and it was perfect and tender. There were 6 pieces!

The roast lamb was just ok. My husband likes the Stephos version better. It was a big chunk of meat though.

As with all greek restaurants, the carbs portion is way too much - rice, potato, and pita. The pita not soft unfortunately.

Definitely would come back for the lamb.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOATDXGeayXLsJ-091SfEA30U9Aiv4xc1ccZC0M&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-8-9"},{"Name":"Jules Wilkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNCphr6IWBKE7mhK1l34cq3DlSdkR802S6gSUfppAdFS2fhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every single item that came was cooked and spiced to perfection. One of the best restaurant steaks I have ever had, the potatoes were surprisingly delicious, the Greek salad had a healthy amount of feta rather than the token shake one normally gets, and everyone else at our table was very pleased with their choices. The price was reasonable and the service friendly. A bit noisy and crowded so nothing to rave about, but nothing to complain about either. The food, being well above average quality, was the reason to immediately leave a well deserved five star review.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TK FIRE","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMwgiWW4CWTw18dhib5ASUUbKOwvxPibgN0xFiOf9nH6Ji-EXH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a great place for Greek food! The atmosphere, and food portions are exactly what I thought of when trying this Greek restaurant and they did not disappoint me at all!

I would recommend this place
The chicken isn't dry it's nice and falvorful. The chicken Santorini is a hearty meal, the beef and chicken souvlaki are great and so is the calamari dinner!

All great foods in a great space! Parking is a bit tricky but there is usually spots available","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtkT9fytHaneOUKAwGkMRNUwRJnYjKLZx-52V1&fid=0x0:0x9833323042c6301"],"When":"2024-7-14"}]

[{"Name":"Sandra Tran Do","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9l6s1YZWB64Ki1thgUudvXKddmLpHe47fEzkyE5Wrayj1VfeG=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a great cozy mom and pops restaurant. it is Italian and Korean fusion. The service here is so good, food was comfort food, it wasn‚Äôt bad but it wasn‚Äôt the best Italian I have had. Would come back tho","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl3P0sP9BMO8A7fcAP--OVyqDEiLIOYcwNgSXd&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"Darian Yee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVa9tIQQ79AzRLuXQPjOsHXO8XmdfzgC67OKlKFj-Hw13RvVc0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don‚Äôt give many five star reviews, and I hope no one sees this one, because I don‚Äôt want my favourite restaurant becoming too busy! The prices are LOW, all plates are around $16. Portion sizes are LARGE, and the food is delicious! We always being left overs home.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO3YidPIFJjE_yahI6LsLC9tA7AzaFHQjR3lrXd&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-11-2"},{"Name":"jen h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhCIsdNpI0zn0ln1R2W8y6FEnO7Rpwo3p2N6L3S94WtNoyzHf7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Truly is a nostalgic joint as I used to go here during high school times. It used to be infamous for their buy two get one free pasta dishes but I believe that deal is no longer available. Regardless of which, they have some great pasta dishes, and are a Korean Italian fusion. You can also adjust spice level if available! They take reservations which is nice for a larger group. Parking is abysmal in that location, but that isn‚Äôt their fault. Usually, I just find parking in the back or on side streets. Most pasta dishes are between $16-$20 and have quite hearty portion and you also get a slice of garlic bread for free. Staff is friendly and usually run by one person but very efficiently.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9jwHT3ikVSlmyrS_uHwj81dsEC0JrFYYYHMr-&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-9-6"},{"Name":"Kamil Chocimski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiqh1VSZRODqN-Djl6vCyrZVFOC1F520DSa-G8lhjPI6NkKSg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Ordered the Caprese salad and Linguine Seoul. The Salad had no Basil, but salad instead. The Mozzarella seams to be defrosted. It falls apart and it's grainy and mush. The tomato slices were very thick and were dry. No flavor. Disappointing.
The Linguine was different. Taste was good, especially the Clams. However I asked for Parmigiano I was given the powdered stuff and not fresh. Also the dish was in a very hot pan, and not a bowl. Got burned a bit. Be careful if you have fidgety hands or nerve damage.
I also had the $5 pink lemonade, which was just pure sugar. Had to squeeze my lemon garnish wedge and dunk it. It didn't help

Service was impeccable, food arrived quick and the server lady was friendly and very helpful. She deserves a raise.

Atmosphere was fine. I love little holes in the wall like this. The booth seat was comfortable. The service and seafood makes up, and I rate it 3 stars.

Pity, because I was looking forward to checking this place for a while. I grew up in Italy and was hopeful. However it's a miss.

Maybe other dishes are better

DO NOT RECOMMEND THE CAPRESE SALAD

I wanted to rate it 2 stars because the food was so disappointing, but despite the lack of fresh ingredients","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGWAfrDYg0ryjkUfLpTX5Rjq44jLrPAuXDilwS&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-8-30"},{"Name":"Caroline *","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8RSBvHYuwmws6j5XyqmPqw1TITZ2sRj-IIy6vhYkGJqRMUR96=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great little gem! I‚Äôve never had a restaurant provide complimentary items, but the lovely server gave me and my friend complimentary garlic bread! ‚ò∫Ô∏è fabulous service. They are very polite and respectful. Often times, I get servers from different restaurants constantly checking up on me every 10 minutes and while I appreciate the effort to ensure we are taken care of, it can get a little uncomfortable. The server here was amazing. She gave us time to enjoy our food, and checked up on us once to ensure our needs were met. I can‚Äôt wait to come back here again!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMl3LyC43s2HkW9spcy0e_cmopO2UBWWXdaJn1O&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-6-5"},{"Name":"Bianca Lok","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWLQf55yrLfuQpaVH5_PAPb-xLqdrIrBA83-7_og5_ndyF7MIm4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have a good selection of dishes on their menu. Each of them look equally delicious. Been there for 2-3 times for lunch, food quality and deliciousness is consistent. Garlic bread is included which is a nice bonus. Portion is sized just enough. Pricing is reasonable and affordable. Otherwise, overall a good place to go if you are looking for decent pasta in the area.
In terms of service, servers do what they need to do and check in to make sure all is good.
It's a good atmosphere as it is never really busy during lunch time, so you can be seated immediately. Also relatively quiet.
The only thing not great is the parking. There is limited street parking, which is pretty much always occupied, but there is a small lot around the corner you can park at and then walk there.

10/10 would recommend to try at least once as their menu will have you going back to try their other food items","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMvJNi4mXTsFlxlVRLuvhRyzXJNyjs0dJLYCKCl&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-2-8"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It's a great Italian place that you should check out if you want to try out some authentic pasta and risotto dishes.

My personal favourite is the linguine soul that comes piping hot and spicy. I also enjoy their seafood risotto that almost comes out like a Spanish paella. The calamari wasn't as good as their pasta dish but still quite tasty.

The garlic bread is a nice little bonus but it's not as fresh as other places. The portions in general are decent and enough to fill you up.

If you're in the area, definitely check them out!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP_9EptdbJrgFN-WlFs_67YFedfhPPA-kuow85D&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-4-23"},{"Name":"Janice Ko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBZdze8bHRgeZWywjB9B830YGMgauY8dm-JU7cYQGuxIUbSKzC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friend brought me here for my birthday last month. The food was surprisingly fabulous. I ordered the seafood pasta, and it was delicious. The staff was very kind. I definitely will bring my family back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOb1O18YubgKwd-WVhAWpPNuheH-vzqyQjFf9UF&fid=0x0:0xae2442bcec231118"],"When":"2024-5-28"}]
