[{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The restaurant‚Äôs set menu is pretty comprehensive with select sliced meats, soup, rice, and salad. We got the couple for two combo despite being three adults as well as a seafood salad and all of that was just the perfect amount of food. The meats were nice and they were easy to cook on the grill. The restaurant had their air con blasting during the summer which helped with all the smoke from the cooking. You can press a button to get a waiter‚Äôs attention. All in all, it was an enjoyable experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMdk7YTvQtA4cOKMVVQglSszfKIHYijWA60r2i2&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Justin J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9qB0BPnH-SxgmMKD9knqz657T2834b2TJgDxXzOsqhmSY7g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"It‚Äôs been a while since I last visited, but the entrance decor remain as memorable as ever. The restaurant offers spacious seating, making it very comfortable. Our server was nice and friendly. The food was good, though the portions are smaller than they used to be. Parking during dinner time remains a challenge and likely will continue to be.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHgVwV-0kvbYUIu3r0xOVfO1OqcnTmIalwcE14&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-12-5"},{"Name":"Fuzzy Nemo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMhjGNDhI-RZYgIiVRXnRDEQCiyyP-dsVjb7EhBkcymNr9MvYi0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I haven't been back here for quite a few years, as I was told that this place have been going downhill.  There are quite a few korean bbq places in the same neighborhood,  I have ventured out.

We had combo B for 2, it was $74.99.  Came worth 4 side dishes, lettuce and many sauces.  The portions are smaller than I remember,  but it was enough for 2 people.   The meat was marinated perfectly and very tasty.

Parking was a little bit of a challenge,  but it depends on the time.

Service was pretty good.  Very attentive and extremely friendly servers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNNRHKGQYZDM4GL10xyomSVDI021HAl5ATqoCfM&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-9-30"},{"Name":"Celine Yin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJa7zO3YqoD-8ECQTGrm6AZLkgEliFXn763fG4QIbn9fdu-Uw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been here 5 times before for special occasions. Recently, we got ourselves a marinated galbi beef rib and seafood pancake. Reasonably priced and authentically delicious. Would high recommend if you‚Äôre in Coquitlam.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPObUplooYfbZDvE2_T9fpjVMbAXZ-keuc1ZTfZ&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-9-8"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Pe√±a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Insadong is definitely one of the KBBQ spots I‚Äôd highly recommend to anyone! The family of 4 combo was incredibly generous, offering a great variety of delicious dishes. The space is inviting and perfect for gathering with friends and enjoying a hearty meal together. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPrRCtpcug4NVf-8gN7TVzxg_s6N8iJkNKMjpiZ&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Eric Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVigEafgSK6F5eAKNdJJYmgUkvkjxBX7FZepIFe9MUzp9yl_4bu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food is overall amazing. The staff are friendly and the people eating around you are very quiet. Which is a good sign if you want to relax and eat some KBBQ. I wish the portion sizes were a little bigger but overall we were pretty full by the end of it. This has to be one of the best KBBQ places in Vancouver.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNgNgbFWrk0xnSlQo7AogFl8DgPzJzf-p0UqnUL&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-10-8"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came back after a while with some friends and had an awesome dining experience.
It was very busy, but we only waited 20 mins to get a seat for 3.
The Meats tasted excellent, as well as the seafood pancake, all the side dishes, and soft tofu soup.
Great customer service too, highly recommend it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipObBfwtCtjZA4QJfrq28hKYBv4oO5yjoq09c9cK&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2023-11-14"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I do like Coquitlam's Korean BBQ restaurant when I'm in the area or have a celebration dinner. Comfortable seating and nice table space. The BBQ combinations are nice and well marinated. I can't emphasize the staff's attentiveness and friendliness. Recommended.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMbm8MjJ1WHW0ijyRUNVqnC7QVmOhJaMN57Sd7&fid=0x0:0x45ad4bc0e24b6787"],"When":"2024-6-24"}]

[{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's a pretty typical dim sum restaurant with decent food and service. I appreciate the speed of the service and the value for all the food. It can get pretty busy, especially during weekends so be prepared to wait if you didn't make a reservation.

We got the lotus leaf wrapped sticky rice with pork, some steamed pea shoots, vegetable porridge (congee) and good selection of dumplings. It's not anything to write home about, but it's hardy and gets the job done. Solid experience overall and I would give them the thumbs up.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNldHIuVK-fsR57KEsIFq08_KeBGOEZKK1j8FvJ&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-17"},{"Name":"Grace Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv2Qb5BK8BlHD8B-fNqpMIiwBP96of3n6s7qsHpu4xPXVSJg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Delicious and cute dim sum! Food was fresh and fast. We made reservations as it can get busy. Staff were friendly and attentive. I do speak Chinese as well. The kids love the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOqxd3kLGHCrMQedJ1T0fOAbSmVa-M_lHRR3aR-&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"Celina Wright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXh2wmxFC5Utlekpzdr2MpXFcBCcrOSjcqSIoXPM9bCTR9ROXAVjw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food was fantastic and the staff were polite.  We visited for dim sum on a weekend. Seating took some time (10-15 minutes) even with a reservation, but I find that to be normal at most dim sum restaurants.

For those unfamiliar with a dim sum restaurant: just make sure you flag down the wait staff if you need anything and they'll head over to you quickly - don't wait for them to check in on you.

We had about 6 dishes among 4 people and were very satisfied with all of them üòå

We had an overall great experience and will visit again soon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPEjZuQIZKRlmVGxE6oDTnZ2lj9iQ_fe2zH2aWD&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Annia Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLCmNf-6kVgoV3z2v1rhLUKPIXQtdwZxPsOxdlb6pZhbXP-BQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoying some yummy üòã dim sum for brunch.

A culinary tradition that has captured the hearts and palates. The term ‚Äúdim sum‚Äù translates to ‚Äútouch the heart,‚Äù a phrase that encapsulates the essence of these bite-sized delights.  So many different varieties of special Chinese dishes, served in small portions for all to share.
Dim sum has always been a symphony of colors, textures, and flavors in each dish to share amounst friends.

Food was fresh and fast service provided. Staff was attentive.  They were busy today luckily made reservations.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPBhObly0gYODvg08E6vPpciOoSHEghCgOJz5-x&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-12-21"},{"Name":"K 2","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCr90XQEGh_XW_dogXGAOrNDNdWl4oto2DcQXyO8hGv5A6DKrVWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I recently had an incredibly disappointing lunch here. We ordered four dishes, but after waiting for more than an hour, only three arrived. The last dish never came despite us repeatedly asking about it. When we requested to cancel the order after an hour, the server responded with an attitude, insisting it was coming. After waiting an additional 20 minutes with no sign of the dish, we had no choice but to cancel it for good.

To make matters worse, the food that we did receive was subpar, tasting like frozen dim sum from T&T rather than freshly made. Seafood roll was.. speechless.. since when the imitation crab became seafood????
The entire experience‚Äîfrom the long wait times to the poor service and bland food‚Äîwas awful. After spending an hour and a half there and only eating three dishes, I was left feeling frustrated and dissatisfied.

I definitely won‚Äôt be returning, and I would not recommend this place to anyone looking for quality dim sum or good service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO797XW5ANvImlqxiyC1g_s4CcDzQenFyWjxZsG&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-9-26"},{"Name":"J T","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhlRzWDXzdsN5IEg7ILK_EQ56zA9jcQ-fPPr3cS5cgV1YVlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Another Neptune afternoon‚Ä¶

I think this is the only Neptune I haven‚Äôt been to yet? Anyways, in the area taking care of some business so decided to try this location out.

It‚Äôs located on the front side of Coquitlam Center and facing the new Cactus Club, plentiful of parking is available up front in the malls parking lot.

Inside is separated into to section; Neptune Wonton for fast casual dishes and Neptune Seafood for more of a formal dining. It‚Äôs kind of a smaller place and pretty basic to me.

Anyways, here were the dim sum I ordered;

1. Seafood dumpling in soup. The imitation crab being used made the broth a bit overly sweet, was too unpleasant to finish it.
2. Steamed spicy beef tripe. It wasn‚Äôt tender enough, needed to steam it a bit longer.
3. Steamed chicken feet with special sauce. It wasn‚Äôt tender enough for the skin to fall off the bone, needed to run through the deep fryer a bit longer during the prep process.
4. Turnip cake with XO sauce. It‚Äôs almost a joke, my 10 year old nephew could‚Äôve done better with this dish especially its presentation. Failed!
5. Baked preserved egg and ginger pastry. Absolutely horrible, the preserved egg was rubbery and the whole pastry crumbled along with its ginger paste. Failed!
6. Fried vegetables with shrimp paste. An alternate version of the deep fried eggplant with shrimp paste. It was so so.
7. Baked bbq pork buns. It was okay, the bbq pork could be less sweet.
8. Purple rice roll with fish paste. It was okay, the super jumbo size was unexpected.
9. Stir fry udon with live lobster. Surprisingly it was pretty good, enough wok hay to really bring out the flavours.
10. Little white rabbit pudding. Not bad, cute little treats.

Overall, I wasn‚Äôt too impressed with the layout and atmosphere of the restaurant. It portray itself as a mid class Chinese seafood restaurant, but felt l like a simple family restaurant with mid level prices.

The service was okay, enough to satisfy the basics, don‚Äôt expect anything more than that.

As for the food, honestly it was probably one of the most disappointing experience I had so far out of all the Neptunes I‚Äôve been to.

Not a repeat or recommendation from me anytime soon‚Ä¶ 1.5 stars","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOQR35TFh2sABn6mWQv4-F7inIjdWxHkqeXqX1w&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2024-6-3"},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Came for dimsum. The portions here are pretty big and taste fresh. Lots of menu items to choose from. We had a larger party (11 people) and they had our table ready on time. However they forgot 3 of our items which we ended up cancelling. Overall good food and friendly service.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM2zar_Z9-rBEtiUz29w_-7yCkOfWbkH7rr9FO8&fid=0x0:0xe8960ddf73ad1704"],"When":"2023-10-9"},{"Name":"CY","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyAWoVXS2wSYA_X8YaMHwhMb74Th2juKHatcW6zvf48kBI0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Been here twice, once in July 2024, once in Nov 2024. Quality difference between a couple months was huge. (Much better food quality and taste now).

Clean and spacious environment.

Food was served a bit slowly though.

Dim Sum dish variety is quite limited on the menu.

Price is a bit higher than mid tier

Over it is decent","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"katayoun fathi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIt4RVxDsU0O9i1saXjwxFzJATudNmH_X0AFWg7oJguKfo6fgs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a very bad experience at that restaurant. There‚Äôs a lady working there as a server ‚Äì the one with glasses ‚Äì and she‚Äôs extremely rude. While I was eating, I witnessed her behaving very disrespectfully toward a delivery driver. It completely ruined my meal, and I couldn‚Äôt even finish it. My spouse and I were sitting there, and we were shocked.

Why should she speak so rudely to a hardworking woman driver, telling her she‚Äôs ‚Äúblocking the way,‚Äù when all the driver did was ask why the food was taking so long? I saw the poor lady standing there for 20 minutes. But the server, a very aggressive girl with glasses, treated her terribly. This is the last time I‚Äôll ever go to that restaurant.

The service was also terrible. That server kept us waiting unnecessarily and didn‚Äôt handle anything professionally.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sokolov Alexey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIdRdPWeIS90ph1aeRePZ6G-sdKlolSkkqu7NaJG2zLuN4gz2N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Calm and nice place. Not crowded, the background music was quiet and not distracting.
Big assortment of fish and seafood.
They serve sushi, nigiri, soup, lots of specialty rolls. Kids bento boxes are available.
I really liked ikura nigiri and rainbow roll.
Roe in ikura nigiri was big.
Staff is friendly but we had to repeat a part of the order a couple of times.
The lunch menu is available only from 15:00.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOtuSD5xezD79_q56e_KtYff_-TzD2Mu7dpwyIV&fid=0x0:0xce9dfb2bfa380a7"],"When":"2023-9-5"},{"Name":"Kevin Kwon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCYT7BU_V3SI2IMbVzmDmEuQkuaR4AJUdkinmJF25w1grdjOYB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Shrinkflation is real. $16 total for a dynamite roll and spicy chopped scallop roll. What has changed?
1. Yam tempura instead of shrimp tempura. Dynamite rolls used to have 2 shrimp tempura IIRC.
2. Less crabmeat, more cucumber. 50/50 split now.
Overall, it isn't the store's fault that costs have risen so much. However, for $16, I feel like the rolls don't provide as much value.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMn7Vi7jFSuwuaGX_trPox4vdYgyGUXBApvtSbH&fid=0x0:0xce9dfb2bfa380a7"],"When":"2024-1-18"},{"Name":"Christi C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcgq9JpIfJ5HaJSvpqHkX5vNrbeeAgd7PrWra2BvtkmNmgVJax=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Food was tasty. Would get the stand-alone tempura again and look forward to trying more on the menu. Vegetables were fresh and crisp. Tempura in the special roll was soggier than expected.

Child was very pleased with post-meal gesture, and we very much appreciated the pleasant surprise.

Personal preference but I felt a bit rushed when asked quite often whether plates were finished with.

Bathroom needs sorting as woman‚Äôs toilet wouldn‚Äôt flush and the restaurant‚Äôs front door is quite heavy to open.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Yim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyAeUh2CClKb5j6bPCfm4WTuRVeJI0Sj2rgBonFkle79yB2OU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A pretty nice neighbourhood sushi restaurant. Friendly, Food is delicious especially if you enjoy the ‚Äúlocalized‚Äù fancy stuff like‚ÄùfFrench Kiss Roll‚Äù etc.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNLkHCqdpt5N8tsA0hz3Dg0FYpPaLFbEEL_1b-P&fid=0x0:0xce9dfb2bfa380a7"],"When":"2023-6-10"},{"Name":"Robert C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWWs1ZuGn1IU9hU9ywiGEtKCQ6RKJwKJrDWc_08WPFhc0a-deo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Our sushi escapade turned out to be more of a comedy than a culinary delight. We ventured into the realm of rolls, bravely ordering a spider roll among others. But alas, as if taking cues from a magician, the sushi rice decided to fall apart before our very eyes. The roll itself seemed to have had an identity crisis, comprising 10% crab, 70% cucumber, and a surprising twist of 20% lettuce. Had I known, I would have simply strolled to Save On, snagged a head of lettuce and a cucumber, and called it a night.

The adventure continued as we discovered that ordering anything with cucumber in this establishment is akin to inviting a vegetable tsunami onto your plate. On the bright side, it's an involuntary dive into your daily greens. Our server, possibly mistaking us for sprinters, could hardly wait for us to finish verbalizing our order before she was off again.

For those seeking real sushi over rabbit food, I'd point you towards Shio Sushi. The quality is night and day and your culinary journey might not feel like a race against time.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuNcE654GNPqVbyj1lDcHP5vwBkA7wbyaXsRmJ&fid=0x0:0xce9dfb2bfa380a7"],"When":"2024-3-5"},{"Name":"Chantelle Ko","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvymNv8m0OjN24OoAK372hJnR2UcKCian5wKRAnKN34mbq8A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"First moved into the area during the pandemic and religiously and frequently ordered takeout and delivery. The food is about a 4/5 on a good day, sometimes a 2-3/5 on an off day.
I have recently started dining in and the service is absolutely horrendous. The servers are unskilled, inexperienced, rude, and snarky. They asked the only white person in our group if he can use chopsticks before we even sat down. The other server was more than reluctant and rude and snappy when trying ask where our appetizer was (already finished our mains) and for more tea. Then she was suddenly sweet and friendly dropping our bill off and taking payment.

After frequenting this restaurant for the last few years, I won‚Äôt be ordering from here anymore.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ariana Abedini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUKNjWemH3JT4c-lZV9IuSCGGzTuGZDPVm9u6xasU8uvx3gj15E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the food! üç£ It's actually the first place I had sushi at my very first time in Canada 6-7 years ago. I'm a regular ever since! The staff is also very polite.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgPo61PA7gsO24pWkqGC4rKCuz7qra5_izX0NO&fid=0x0:0xce9dfb2bfa380a7"],"When":"2022-10-1"}]

Plus, it‚Äôs really convenient to get to, which makes it even better. I‚Äôll definitely be coming back for more and will recommend it to anyone looking for a great KBBQ experience!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlaWj3dvcIl5rjA8xHYEay87yo5cmMOOpdyjpo&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2024-12-8"},{"Name":"Hanif M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUffyC8zNMufrv130HoQIUZhrgzgxk_iDPTgtNVSsLcoEZ6LvtH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Loved this little place for a quick lunch. The Bulgogi was really delicious and all of the sides they bring improved the dish. The kimchee was very tasty and the service was courteous and efficient. Will go back for sure.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNv9xQ5gOYRPyY8AHCbMMP0PnUzkKryngvTUMde&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2024-11-12"},{"Name":"K‚Äôs coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Heard of this Korean BBQ restaurant for a long time. Finally have a chance to visit. Our experience is good. Meat quality is fresh and good cut. Marinated meat taste very good üëçüèª. Love the Korean preserved radish side dish. (We asked for refill). Servers are very nice with smiles always. If they can come to check on us more to refill hot tea and remove extra plate that will be great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN8WjM559y3VhluTR4eECQe-jmQ0q672d683sJW&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2022-9-13"},{"Name":"Rebecca P.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOtv1z9oQXsu_j8G9uE8jVQGZlbdGZfOgnrsP8gOev0iFfifM3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very good prices for the quality and quantity of meat! Under $30 for most bbq plates. Heads up, if you want beef belly, there is a requirement to order min 2 plates.

Their pork jowl was very fatty and thick, which was a surprise as most places give you thin pieces. I enjoyed their beef tongue as well. Everything paired up nicely with thier sauce and sides.

1 star off as service was not attentive. We had reservations and took forever for someone to seat us. We had to awkwardly flag a server down to take our order and they never came back to check on us until we were ready to pay.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCknPI7zYS3JLALNos8BcHsOSPESlo-5WdSFHC&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2023-6-6"},{"Name":"Gina Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWUEH2BZpcTzOQnjuTeyPiJYzBdsA8VUMp3qYAeuxgNC4m6LJux0g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went Haan with my sister today for lunch. They have a Lunch special for $20. I was surprised with all the dishes served. We ordered pork galbi special. There are Japchea ( noodle) and kimchi pancakes and 6 side dishes. All of them tastes good. Japchea was a bit salty. Tofu soup was enough for two people. We ordered veggie wrappers with extra charge but cannot be missed. It served good amount of lettuce and they were fresh. I will be back for Bulgogi special to try on my next day off. Too bad special menu is only for weekdays lunch.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMVLZhiDsqeTrQwaFRuviaOGjZew40zxjUGKvFC&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2023-7-15"},{"Name":"Adrienne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvS1YiBi1kAYmplCTkzo9NqyjbLMViYayHxaEQA-dKyQUyyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We‚Äôve been coming to HAAN‚Äôs for the last few years, and we always have a great time! Korean BBQ is great for socializing and it‚Äôs a fun experience. Our server was very nice and friendly. We love their beef tartar and cold noodles. The sliced pork belly is also one of our go to‚Äôs, but we found it sliced a bit thinner this time. We do find it a little pricey, and they‚Äôve started to charge for lettuce refills.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP5cUEhhBiNS7NzPkL-UHB_O6Ja5DwMWULnGQdc&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2023-5-22"},{"Name":"Kristy Chen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWEfZ2rjxNiODjhooQ3vu4wU52UFmMssx1nBEw-QrGtiP3D8nPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The meat here was okay, but nothing special. The side dishes were a tad lacking and there was a weird aftertaste to the soup. The seafood pancake was not great either. I would not recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNR10nrBSV-NSZC5ntuOw2D73lo36RWKfk0gvs5&fid=0x0:0x2f8ab8e80275082"],"When":"2024-3-21"}]

We are definitely coming back here soon.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPPJ615wqd2CrHXFNFYjjcgfZnyLiMPdyrFMFv9&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2024-11-16"},{"Name":"Maria M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIbAl3QqzjCkGeEfZrvLw1-pFOjmS4Pev33ZP0gmGTUa7cdX1E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My hubby and I came in for a late dinner.  We were greeted by Anna with a cheerful smile, led to our table and after some talk she took our order.  We haven‚Äôt been to this location so she gave us some very good suggestions,  hubby took the original hamburger and I got the senior 3 course meal,  cream of mushroom soup, chicken strips with coleslaw and lemon meringue pie.  Glad we took her suggestions.  We enjoyed our meal.  Everything was cooked to perfection.  The ambiance was great and the restaurant was so clean.   It‚Äôs really amazing what you learn unexpectedly just by talking to people like Anna, who served us and the other young lady. And even though it was close to closing time, we did not feel rushed.  All in all we had a great experience and being creatures of habits, we will surely be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWItgijJKwgA0f52g38y2veJk-Ddfx32Y6n5pRa8jqM3m7RR0lStA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very casual and cozy atmosphere similar to a pub.  Service was slow to begin with but ended up being good. Wasn't excellent per se but good.

Their omelette was cooked well. I like how their veggies had a bit of a crunch to them. Perhaps the peppers could have been cooked slightly longer but it was good. Shredded hash browns were not greasy which was good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"K‚Äôs coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This is my first time here and it was not a pleasant experience. I have studied the menu ahead of time and was looking forward for my dinner gathering with one extra family. Not sure if our server is new to her job.  After taking our order and we all confirmed the detail. Number of things went wrong.  First we ordered a soup (meal size) with garlic bread. It came in a cup size instead (no bread). We also ordered a burger with lettuce wrap. This option was highlighted on their menu. We explained to the server few time and make sure she understands. She end up giving us a burger with bun. We asked for and exchange and it came back with literally just TWO pieces of lettuce ü•¨
If you have a lettuce wrapped burger elsewhere  you should know how‚Äôs that should be (Very disappointed). We also ordered a kid meal. The server didn‚Äôt offer any drink until we remembered that was included. Overall the food was blend and the server knowledgeable need a big improvement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGZG4BlkpSSw-LeSXPzH0zwtq3X1vPWfh9cJ40&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2023-3-9"},{"Name":"Al So","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLumQHIv-5W9wXPr4ZbA1zWCVnPk2w1Kc3bjsO93-VMG-v7JQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"One of the few places in the area for  breakfast. Place was busy for a Saturday morning. This used to be an ABC restaurant but it closed, owner was ready for retirement and the Ricky's down the street closed and moved to this location. So even less options to eat out breakfast. Food was as expected and good options for kids. There is an interesting private room at the back good for parties and large groups. No issues I would eat here again,","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNxUWJfMLXiAJVaB7hhn8uxnbyOd8XorXIM4AT1&fid=0x0:0x6154d88775c17540"],"When":"2022-10-23"}]

[{"Name":"Sam Goh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE5mTKD61HIgHQk8dxPyuoRqeGbk2g-M7HwnIwadO5n9CEZ1k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hons is an authentic casual Chinese restaurant. They make everything to order and have an extensive menu. When we go, our fav 3 dishes are the BBQ fried rice, tofu with rock salt as well as the black pepper chicken with broccoli.  When ordering we usually ask them to withhold the black pepper sauce on the chicken with broccoli as sometimes we find that it‚Äôs too much sauce.

We have previously had other dishes such as wontons, sweet and sour pork, eggplant, hot and sour soup, mixed veggies, Shanghai noodles etc and have enjoyed those as well. There really isn‚Äôt anything we didn‚Äôt like.

Service is typical Chinese restaurant style so don‚Äôt be shy to flag the servers down as they can get busy.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNSoq4VSBcm5D9NiPXkZE-eK_-qTsSJ4cK7Mq7j&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Hon's on Coquitlam is one of my go to to pick up a quick dinner. I usually pop in and check out the presented BBQ and roasted duck, pork and chicken in the display. I am always greeted by friendly staff and my food is always up to standard.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYt6ZGXk07h2TuGo8zKEaxdScTRMp_5YeuJkyR&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-7-21"},{"Name":"Damaris Ibarra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX94ja2TK604xuamsF18bxzGKPd7B1_MlnXlwCnslYshD_71-qX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I went to Hon‚Äôs Wun-Tun House yesterday for the first time in about a year or two. I was very disappointed and surprised when I had realized the flavour of the food had gone downhill. I used to love Hons cause they used to have Good portions and amazing flavour for a good price however, things have turned for the worse recently and now even the cheaper TNT meals you can get at the mall tastes better than the food on this day.

The wonton soup was super salty and tasted very fishy which i‚Äôve never experienced in a wonton soup before (i love wonton soup so that was surprising that it tasted so wierd). I also ordered the beef and brocoli crispy Chow Mein, which is no longer on their menu but the lady said they could make it which is why I gave them a high rating for the service. The chow mein (the whole thing including the beef) tasted a bit wrong like if it shouldn‚Äôt be eaten. Not sure how to describe the flavour but it just tasted off and wrong to eat. It was not the flavour I had known and loved hons for, instead it tasted wierd. I am incredibly disappointed that one of my previous favourite chinese food spots no longer have good flavour and have gone downhill. We did order other things as well and honestly the only thing i liked from this whole meal is the rice.

I will be on the search for better chinese food restaurants because i‚Äôm so sad and disappointed that this one won‚Äôt hold up to a good standard anymore. The service was really good however and they were very quick, efficient and kind so good job on the service. It was the food that was a big turn off. I hope they are able to bring back their old good flavour they used to have in their food and improve on the quality and flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOeS2mABL7p7eLR9gTvg-74i-iEn4ZW4T_qAG3o&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Nona SM","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfjTMq2ZKlGJ4Ldu_6g6I_gZ33bv-9-UjHyDYxTjehH_EmHBBS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We would rate this restaurant 0 star if we could, The portions are big, but the smell of the food is horrendous so you will not even get to eat the food. It‚Äôs sticky and the vegetables are discoloured (the broccoli is grey and yellow‚Ä¶)
We ended up letting them know how bad everything was and it was definitely a health hazard to consume and still had to pay full price which is very disappointing.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOo4rv95AaM88dKIuaKfG1oWNhlnzblsWhNADeb&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-28"},{"Name":"Maxine No√´l","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQMYs4r5B33gJ34fAugWWfmH6Yn9m7uwjCQYiizbCj9u8j9fk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So delicious, definitely authentic quality Chinese food and the best sweet and sour pork you'll ever have. It's crunchy on the outside and coated in that sticky sweet sauce. The way they flame wok their dishes just adds so much flavour.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNT4VmTkah8-MppOfU_gvgGtyfVeJikEwnT9Pr4&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2023-8-3"},{"Name":"Alissa willman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEDSWOUv6R8DeP9mxksuJk54LZ_0QYAbltxQmHt531hSIGfalIYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Ohmygosh I almost don't want to leave a review as if I do it will bring attention to this secret gem and possibly drive the price up. The food is sooo good! And the servings are HUGE!!! DEFINITELY coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNDvBEFlpu-jSgA6qY8f_CpsWkpIMw0YDcxqRiW&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-3-31"},{"Name":"Daniel HAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIChGR0mPBUiK47gPt8g99ilcJC6KXSWmFux6ml52TbewOKlQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This restaurant uses low quality ingredients and the food smells weird.

The worst problem is that the servers are very rude. If you order a little bit, they keep staring at you and being rude. I will never go to this restaurant again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMeR1bHYASQgCSg0QnrgKxMtvU9u-NClGdjdbCU&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2024-9-1"},{"Name":"Candice C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwFBBjzDK0K147Ahvw56fgZp0Wzk8W8u0zo_aJQ425Hu_MYA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Haven't ordered from Hons in a long time, decided to get food through uber eats. The food was delivered well within the estimated time and the food was very good. Not a lot of places offer a cod and tofu (bean curd) hotpot but this place does. üëå","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMix90dzMRR_ADqZX-pPRXF85N35NSNq9TqWZbe&fid=0x0:0x95ff28cd48bec56f"],"When":"2023-5-22"}]

Glad I did. We could use more people caring for our communities. ‚ù§Ô∏è","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7P_p5bi-KKlj17E6nrpIy_8Qw1DZ6FIr7Gun5&fid=0x0:0x6a0dbb1d99a6ada2"],"When":"2024-5-18"},{"Name":"JR","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK3_YGWEMNJWYNkYPArm1lJ_HP7RyEaBVSqqscwHuICtS_M=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolutely garbage "Greek" food, if you can call it that. I can tell whoever is in the kitchen is guessing at what Greek is supposed to taste like and they have no culinary skill at all, none, zip, ziltch. Stop selling this food immediately. It belongs in the trash. Sorry not sorry you shouldn't be selling this, you're ripping people off.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Byron Lin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1ZIkhKMx6Jhytrhte_ByMuWA-wf7fxdgXGR0uc8XVcrVhDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great middle eastern food at affordable prices.

Got their beef shami lunch special with a mango lassi for $15.

Tasted great and good portions. Owners were nice as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOhcQk43-JRrjVLW-AoompYCS-XyyjI2JjL3NO3&fid=0x0:0x6a0dbb1d99a6ada2"],"When":"2023-12-27"},{"Name":"v","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMalQNO5O3WgU0LxOYrpn0-JYQ9ou7NIB8ukVrbj1B_A3Hleze=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Sorry.......not great. We ordered the butter chicken and naan. The butter chicken had the consistency of tomato soup and frankly the flavour to match. Way to runny. I will say the actual chicken in the dish was nice, not too dry, but they hardly give you any. The naan was a bit on the chewy side. We are going to stick with our old faithful which is strictly Indian food. This place may offer too many styles of food which may mean they are just mediocre making all of them instead of being fantastic with one style. We don't recommend nor will we be ordering anything from them in the future... even though we only had the Indian since it was mediocre we are going to have to assume the rest is as well. I almost forgot... we ordered a piece of cheesecake as well..it was horrible, I actual think it had gone off and they smothered it with all this sweet sauce to cover it up. DISGUSTING. I hope we don't end up sick from the few bites we had before we realized there was something up. If I could give this place zero stars I would.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnBSkxO-LuBP1CDOgiqV7Ke19lsi_tq2kPrRFW&fid=0x0:0x6a0dbb1d99a6ada2"],"When":"2021-8-9"},{"Name":"Jonathon Gagnon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWthbVfHKE36MOK846jxUfBzBByHNknTZyAsz0C7lTAOrW=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Absolute trash. $30 lamb roast mostly fat. Hard potatoes Rude staff member when I called. We have much better options in the tri cities. Wish I could get my money back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8BlmH2-mClq09VJ4q5kh6UailoOk9lZYvwcel&fid=0x0:0x6a0dbb1d99a6ada2"],"When":"2023-6-14"},{"Name":"Liam Moss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZPZS67TQqx3Uea76ERA7BRjgSHA5yKUONJDHUOaBBanw5cV7a9w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Their curry‚Äôs are unbelievable, as a Brit living in Canada I really miss good curry. The Pakistanis and Bangladeshis who run our Indian restaurants in the UK do a great job. The Indians who run the Indian restaurants here do a terrible job both in value and quality. Forgive me if I‚Äôm wrong but I believe these guys are Afghan, who have far more in common culinary wise with Pakistan and hence they make much better curry then Sirdaarjii. Bravo, I can‚Äôt wait to come back. Amazing value too with the lunch special, great for a work lunch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Cima","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7L4JEMxZTTSVa9798NKuFVKr18jcX25PgN9UVVk9MTGHQaVg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hidden gem for Middle Eastern and Indian food in Coquitlam. [{"Name":"Broskyy7473 46","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4v-9NWNOaL2o-ob1QwNNXkaRai8pnmHjOOf8lsjZnA0uYMYVv=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza here is always fantastic..
Best I‚Äôve had
Always come back to La Ruota for some great slices
Carne Picante is incredible..","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPTviU8tBh3XBdEINTzCfpD-_30eazxmTHxKOOV&fid=0x0:0xb28c6c54cf384b07"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"Brina Wellington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW_igXj_VFA6UN-NlH930Gh3dSaeG7ma1g0O3gBgnWDbUwpazzf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"The pizza guy said 20 but it took 40 minutes to get our pizza. To me this is eat it right away pizza it does not benefit from sitting in a box the thin crust gets soggy fast that said it was good we ate in front of the place so it was fresh","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPNyz-K_LOnJEAbWNNubKqUE48RU7cjAZt2ZLIu&fid=0x0:0xb28c6c54cf384b07"],"When":"2024-6-12"},{"Name":"Amy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVOcU52bOwjYSEbSJ2t4-mBspc4KO3qf3ZMty8mlhHcMGCJeSoC=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Me and my family ordered on too good to go (for those of you who don‚Äôt know it‚Äôs an app that allows restaurants to serve food that was not sold the previous day for cheap) and we have been on the app for a while enjoying the treats. We‚Äôve also been fans of La Ruota for a while but today when we got our order we were so disappointed with the quality of the pizza. 3 slices of the 6 slices were so burnt that it only makes sense that the workers would have thrown it away but instead they decided to still sell inedible garbage. The only silver lining is that there were 3 slices that were okay, but it‚Äôs appalling that these slices were even considered for consumption. I‚Äôm all for saving leftovers and food, but this was so disappointing.

UPDATE: I don‚Äôt think you guys understand my issue. I‚Äôm not talking about how fresh the pizza is, I‚Äôm not talking about how the pizza wasn‚Äôt the exact same as freshly made pizza, I‚Äôm talking about how you guys burnt pizza, and then served it to people. That is unacceptable as a restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN94MzId_piwY4RNlX_BBvjMOOLFgr-N7mGMwNK&fid=0x0:0xb28c6c54cf384b07"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"Danny D","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMy7cZTSIOMfwAmDoTnpYDFtZXeJmLNdRr4FkFM73bVHc0TxGV1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I‚Äôve been ordering and visiting La Ruota Coquitlam since the original Italians opened it many many years ago.  Since these new owners took over the pizza and service have gone down hill tremendously. Quality downhill, price uphill.  I always order additional toppings of arugula for example and I swear it never comes on it. They say they‚Äôre busy as an excuse. Maybe if they just read the order like a kindergarten student can and you‚Äôll get the order right. Long time customer. Management and staff need to do better. How hard is it to ask for this? Disappointing is an understatement.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"samuel suarez pineda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIHKr-_yToakG57E86Bb_8G5a4CUCMIPQbdus_gWzlhzsNYMeILg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The pizza was amazing, the flavor is really delicious, the people that work here are very kind, the best flavor for me was carne picante","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO9BSzM3S2j1rLZtvxvmYF-OX-Pgde5k5jBXWsP&fid=0x0:0xb28c6c54cf384b07"],"When":"2024-8-18"},{"Name":"Viona Halim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV5PMLEtvgkAwv2IjmL8XXm0-Ly_XpBo5Kd0Hv2pxoQ26_Hfy4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It's a different thin crust option for take out pizza if you don't feel like having more of the doughy usual in the likes of Panago, Dominos, Fresh Slice, etc. But that's just it, it's a take-out quality pizza so don't expect anything mind-blowing.

The venue is definitely a step above your usual pizza joint. It's more modern and cozy looking. By the slice, costs about ~$4 /slice or so. If you just want a few slices to eat there, they would warm up the ones on the display for you. I think because they've been sitting on the display and got warmed up, the dough lost that elasticity and chewiness compared to fresh made pizza, but that's really unavoidable for anything that's been sitting on display counter. So maybe you'll get better ones if you order a whole pan size","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPhpUwfzSgIbma1gXxX-xq7pW3KnglGrDRRkUyK&fid=0x0:0xb28c6c54cf384b07"],"When":"2022-11-5"},{"Name":"Daniel Jung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFE7g6vnjf23CW6mDeh4anchF8fxBs6O5Nsx0bvhepuO3MVzWa=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Update:
Was invited back and wow!! I was recommended the Bugogi pizza, and it was heavenly! (Just look at the photo) The ribeye was juicy, and the bugogi flavor was spot on with a kick of heat.. I truly enjoyed every bite and tasted why La Ruota has a high rating. I will definitely be back for the Bugogi pizza and to try the other flavors of their pizzas.

The owner truly cares for the customer's experience and making delicious premium pizzas!

*They also had live music when I came in Friday night. The vibe was üëåüèª

Reviews brought me here, but unfortunately, the taste didn't do it for me.. For me, the pizza was so sweet.. The pizza sauce was overwhelmingly sweet for me.. I got the Primo with Vegan cheese.

user_reviews:
[{"Name":"Frank Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_FRblBfSgHTr-UE0tiLX-XMrs2VlygGYnC4upIgoM9g7vtg6H=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid kbbq in Coquitlam. The meat was fresh, and the side dishes were good. We got our food within minutes of ordering, but the stove had to be kept on a very low setting and it took a while for the meat to cook. We didn‚Äôt mind it, though, because we used the time to chat and enjoy the side dishes.
Service was decent, as the staff responded right away to the call button. However, the thermos for the hot water was too small for the entire table, and it had to be refilled a few times.
The location is somewhat confusing. From the parking lot, we had to walk past 4 locked doors to the restaurant before finally reaching the correct one. We almost thought that the restaurant was closed and left for something else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOkajA8nD6IHNby0VZDr8e_gafmmLjFgwNAGS22&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-11-11"},{"Name":"Kevin Luo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWJMxLZr-3YvPOYEYkCwOqoRgX8yyWGLPYZ19IJEKzgIUssXc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After dining here several times, I definitely owe this place a review. The food here has been excellent every time. Their meat for Korean BBQ is always fresh, marbled, and of the top quality. I had an Anago (eel) combo meal this time, and portions are massive. The eel was tender and super flavourful. The banchan was plentiful and the selection was great. The yogurt was a nice touch as well. I enjoy dining here and would not hesitate to come back again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM45iDDA28LOHZSBXEfeQwHa80yiZgDvE1SzOWH&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-12-7"},{"Name":"K‚Äôs coffee lover","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-385uQOflrqOxsV0QWsdIyhv-rxdZ7rLwLnLPmzpfPGzr9P6Z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had heard so many positive comments about the lunch set here, so I finally had the chance to visit on a weekday. From the moment I walked in, the service was excellent. I was seated right away, and throughout the meal, the staff checked in regularly to ensure everything was to my liking and even offered refills on the side dishes.

The hot stone rice bowl set menu was especially tempting, with a variety of options including grilled fish, beef short ribs, vegetarian dishes, and even Korean soy-marinated raw crab and shrimp‚Äîdishes that were hard to resist. Each hot stone rice bowl set comes with flavorful Korean side dishes and a daily soup, which is always one of the highlights of Korean cuisine. On this visit, I was offered a spicy beef and silky tofu soup, which was both rich in flavor and incredibly comforting.

For the main course, I enjoyed a whole crab and two prawns. To make it easier, they provided disposable gloves for handling the crab shell. Curious about the best way to enjoy the meal, I asked the server for a recommendation. She suggested removing the crab meat, mixing it with the hot, steaming rice, adding an egg yolk and flying fish roe, and then topping it all off with toasted seaweed. The result was fantastic‚Äîrich, flavorful, and incredibly satisfying!

Overall, the experience was a perfect blend of great food, attentive service, and a memorable meal.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfQ0DUcbW3jtlTCqTJslbdoDJSbOkQ7SoIXn6E&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-11-8"},{"Name":"Jessameen Dela Pe√±a","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9mRpmL8-ZJUG7UPFcnsjzRdxjABif-MswbO1rxgJyyWfns8Jd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We enjoyed the Kosoo Combo C for 2, which included Beef Short Rib, Marinated Beef Short Rib, and Marinated Pork Galbi. The experience was great with ample side dishes and the ease of ordering via screen. Service was efficient, and though it was a bit pricey, we left feeling fully satisfied. Plus, it's just a 7-minute walk from Lincoln Station, making it very accessible. I highly recommend this place!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP2oI0_Xuy51sCWwB8XTmtNHBjUma0Dudnu4b6Z&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-8-24"},{"Name":"Jim Fong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3tXWnX8xFhA_qZcSgIAVcjedjNVtb5Riz6aB4ltUNzTkDmgfU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for Korean BBQ in Coquitlam.

Ordered the Kosoo Combo B for 2 and it was more than enough for my wife and I. The Marinated LA Galbi was sooo tender and tasty. We found the Marinated Rib Fingers a little on the chewy side for us.

The Original Boneless Chicken was OK. Tender and crisp but not much flavour to it. Got scared away when the Soy Garlic Boneless Chicken said ‚Äúmildly spicy‚Äù. üòÇ I can‚Äôt handle anything spicy (even mild) ü§£

They were kind enough to give my wife a side of Kosoo Sweet Chili Sauce for the chicken. üëç

Word to myself: Don‚Äôt sit next to the window in the summertime during sunset. The sun coming through the window was pretty hot. Even hotter when you‚Äôre doing BBQ. üòÇ

Will definitely be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMiiZOETe1b9bXadFoLQWTHGT4aVwaNe7n8pjxb&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Danny Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8eoyUE6az-FmQo7i2mVq5z64Ow48sgKu1EmLZc0zWWN6DMy5asw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A decent experience. Korean-style on-table ordering tablets. The lunch BBQ sets are actually a pretty good deal, but the soups they come with fell a bit flat. The side dishes are unlimited but also tasted a bit too mass produced.

The service was great though and super responsive. The servers helped us navigate the menus and give us the best value which was much appreciated.

Overall food was a bit meh but the meat was good at a good, value price point. Rice is NOT included in the lunch BBQ set so that‚Äôs where they kind of get you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOUuQRlLttE2XKuuZohO8egDeUJkmJtGMowI6W_&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-6-26"},{"Name":"Selena B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9oMe3hVhXNDIiZtsRCJWTyPzsoA7vS6BX-uuHALmBEK2jiw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Commuted long to visit this location because it came up on the Instagram reel that they were offering a $15. When we asked about it, the waiter said it was no longer available and that the influencer must have reloaded an old video? Ended up paying $7 more for what was advertised as $15 which is fine but the principle is not clear. I just checked the website
and it says $15 ??? Especially if I could have gone elsewhere closer to home for the same hot stone set meal. Staff are nice and attentive but we felt played to have even come all the way to Coquitlam. Parking is also paid if you park in the lot.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOpa7fc6dpQj5YZxvRzY0BVDNQzgj9FFQcXI89p&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-12-16"},{"Name":"Minjie Woo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX9zCbBrt4O1rQ26qjjR37DSEbPG4bZnbwCbIMdl20MdB7NZLPy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"We went to try their hot stone bowl set that has been advertised online (through their instagram and TikTok) as well as their current menu to have a variety of side dishes.  We ordered the fried Mandu to start and that was very good. For mains, I ordered the bulgogi hot bowl set and my partner ordered the spicy pork hot bowl set. The main bowls were delicious for both sets. However, they advertise this to be with a variety of banchans (Korean side dishes) and to be honest..I was excited for the banchans. To my disappointment, it came with the absolute bare minimum- kimchi, bean spout salad (you can get these for free at literally any traditionally korean restaurant), and cold jeon. I think the salad was just to fill the tray. The ‚Äúdaily soup‚Äù was also disappointing; there were literally just slivers of radish and fish cakes. I was expecting something more substantial, even something like ÎêúÏû•Ï∞åÍ∞ú. Maybe they felt pity for this sad tray of banchans bc they put a random bottle of yakult on there as well. I really hope that the restaurant takes this review into account and goes back to serving what they advertise online and on their menu.

Please see the sad reality vs online ads of their hot stone bowl sets. Just so sad and disappointing :(","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAbsIVgMhpHsUr_OPN5y7pGoXy98WT1Ywvh2_Q&fid=0x0:0x6e59361dade417d0"],"When":"2024-12-8"}]

[{"Name":"Fat Cook Papa (Fat Cook Papa)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUpgi6nqSgMlDhQ45Yjl_gk21krVh2zgBl_CxlCp6gK1X_Jg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Coming from Toronto..

Love and enjoy great views from the patio.

Fish and Fries - both of their batter and fries were overpowdered and little salty. Also, I'm quite disappointed with the fries portion.
Unfortunately, two pieces of COD were first serving. Apparently, they looked like cooking with different preparation timing. One was great with thick cut crunchy exterior and soft interior, other piece hasn't fully fried to perfection. It's greasy and less crispy.

The Downtowner Pizza - pleasantly surprised by the amazing flavor honey drizzle on pizza. The heat of the pizza then warm the honey as it mixed with the sauce and toppings.

Wings - no impressed.¬† Originally ordered with Honey garlic sauce toppings style.
Unfortunately, wings were made with buffalo style and tasted like they half coated them with tobasco by mistaken.

We have to say they were by far some of the worst wings I have ever eaten. It's tasted like korean BBQ fried chicken wing.

A little bit pricey and service does need a lot of improvement.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP0be5JHmIITlNBtCmwiDVXPzfNar9iOeCiuLah&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-6-4"},{"Name":"Amy Adams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWyVH38TT4RWGwG_4hraWZRuXvb1BELFJJQ_LmMrQJEwE8qxzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Salted and pepper Wings are hard and dried, only drumette, no wingette. So disappointed.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOR5_ZcPVXhC0Wp4WEPzD8P0o66YgMQsBgVyxdG&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Bekah French","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJiYLh-7emQ9AthzE2N_CGxwmtRUdZguPeMRuVIWmhyOtllxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Views and location are amazing. Would love to visit again in the summer and sit out on their big patio we ordered the soup of the day (chicken and vegetable), it was okay. And we shared a meat lovers pizza. We requested half with no cheese (for me) but the pizza came out first time incorrect (it was half cheese only, half meat). They quickly remade the pizza and the base was very yummy. I‚Äôd rate the pizza as a whole 3/5. We found the service very friendly and welcoming.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNwfumHC1VMOXhld8Vw1mT60IYGLKPdkLMIuntT&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2022-11-16"},{"Name":"Ali Mehrizi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWq9cg0fjpkngwNGme387YM4kRUdnI6Pf_Z33gzbG1mkoqze49=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Beautiful views of town (all the way to Burnaby) and good pub food. Fries were one of the best I have had. Drinks are good and beer flights are generous. A quick and good place if you‚Äôre in the more residential part of northern Coquitlam.

I just wish the service was more courteous. We had to wait quite a bit to get our server‚Äôs attention when we wanted to order extra food and drinks. When the food came (in reasonable time), she came to check on us only when we were almost done. On the bright side, I don‚Äôt think this is the service culture at Fairways; the two other persons who helped us sit and get a clean/sanitized table were very nice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4yxOEC8MmM2niMejhmuf8tooer3a0pejf_8Sj&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2020-10-22"},{"Name":"Janice Robinson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwXAghB0kKeZJUcp8jSMN3IavGDPtUMtF57yQo1h9gD5800GlzTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The last time I dined at this restaurant, it was called Hazards, and we lived 5 minutes away.  Having moved 10 years ago, it was nice to return to a familiar place. The service was pleasant and timely, and the 3 of us really enjoyed our meals.  I had the blackened salmon tacos, which were very flavourful and expertly prepared. I will definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eun R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtFP78dUqzbrC3sUP2EUQ7OgKF-9eTaViByIOG1MgbwrrOyEABLw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Food quality is good, portion is generous, and servers are friendly and attentive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMYiB0HybsweJ0t28YswxQYL6q4xyemOS01_F9f&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2024-7-23"},{"Name":"Ve7123","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI37Dp_jMOGKDkNZyR_8bRIASwIfCrsxmFZJBEVbUjSJ5H-kA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I am living nearby ,we're always coming here.
Today, we ordered the pizza of The downtowner, and it looks like only the dough, where the cheese and meat are.
I suggest that if there is no price increase, please cancel this item, because it is like deceive  customers, the goods are not right.
Quality has no standard

Yesterday we came again.
Because the design and atmosphere of the restaurant are good. However, we only ate for half an hour, and the waitress often came to urge and disturb the guests. Points will be deducted for this.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPFDpA3izzm0cCAL6kBKdFvDio1yiFbqIA-zvUu&fid=0x0:0xbbadd84419ac02a9"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Reza Abbaszadeh Hassiri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK26XcBa9A6TQLl_HXySTSrhIoetCnYiLUxzi8E55Bm8P9Z1A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just started hanging out there, I tried soup and fries twice already and Today I took coffee and cheesecake. Never got disappointed so far. You can put nice service and staff on top of that. Ariana is one of the best! Good atmosphere and view as well!!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Kimiya Namdar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5NoUG9m0kwHJtkvaDA-UHALghW-sRI1Mo4nWzPLFWn5wQUVw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"For our anniversary, we decided to stay local and chose Cactus Club, and it didn‚Äôt disappoint. We arrived 15 minutes early but were seated promptly. Moe, our host, was attentive and made sure we were well taken care of. We both ordered the steak, which was delicious and came in generous portions. When it came time to settle the bill, we were pleasantly surprised to find that our dessert was on the house‚Äîa thoughtful gesture for our special occasion. It‚Äôs the little touches like these that make all the difference.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOlxtSajFGYkpR7ks7zBaxq3E_Rq1AoW205uJz3&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-11-3"},{"Name":"Jennifer Bee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFO0fgPBTIA1yxL3IXSghRJ6EmshLC1YB1a72b-xeg3kpjHx0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Date night with my husband. I got the lemongrass prawns and he got the garden burger with Parmesan fries. No picture, but we also got the chocolate peanut butter bar which we love and have ordered several times before. Service was alright but not outstanding.

Edit: we‚Äôve been back several times and always great food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNz5o-NfFrzlsDuL1toQAzF3vym_4Nh0sKHc_Lp&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-7-14"},{"Name":"Jordan Ho","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW11-xeEA0Ih57ocfphXt0C50QwI614ll6t2qknklEqHoDt3aVy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Solid cactus club location; nice atmosphere and decor. Consistent and stable restaurant chain location if you‚Äôre looking for food in the area.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipM7JfFoNjTGrrXQsFLHbl5e01TNdKb9RpDU_IFL&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-10-14"},{"Name":"Karl San Ramon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWMltI1k0x7sCrxqWzfGjhhl5muphr65hDnGIRaggxIcR7yfMIR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cactus Club has a great atmosphere and excellent customer service. I highly recommend trying the Grilled Dijon Salmon!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNl92y_vb_FdIj60kUcUGAjZPOYeXYYPKVGDMhf&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-9-29"},{"Name":"KANVAS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc7GQRe5cyMmMtBU7rwkkBMqSxMQC9wVOgxESX-9VBPO4cx_Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Im not one to go chain restaurants, given it was my first time and was highly recommended by friends. Overall the food was beautifully presented and favourites were well balanced. Toronto your better not let me down your new location is next!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMA1QrmgM-GyOZ24ZLj9F_eDXwNVUXstwreB7rT&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-10-1"},{"Name":"L V","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbiBK61CfZsFrw4Y5hmNaYU_dtvifHPnmGFELAVcKqQqcdlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We did not make a reservation but we did not have to wait too long to be seated. It is a busy location but the ambience and music is great. We had the Hot Chicken and Pickles, Szechuan Lettuce Wraps and Truffle Parmesan Chicken. Love the combination of the spicy chicken and Pickles. The lettuce wraps were a little too sweet for my liking but it is a great portion size. The Truffle Parmesan Chicken is amazing. All in all it was a great meal, excellent service and ambience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQyUeOozUAESqYwdONgFOXK7yBuKkPRnZnhibN&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"MAY Îß§Ïù¥ Elford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxJVIiA7BVVmzUGqT6sRzP7-hCdYJttIOnYMeIvWOWZPmq7cr7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Celebrated a birthday üéÇ and the birthday card on the table was a lovely touch. The free dessert with a candle was superb! Thank you for making it special.
Our server was friendly and great!
No problem with ordering and food came out quick and perfect.
Even with someone who had a difficult dietary restriction, the server managed to accommodate my friend. She also managed to get my drink request done!
Thank you! Keep up the good work! Hope we can reserve again for our next visit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipND9CuiRPSHeu1y7A29JkMA03atMeWruLWhVzkM&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-5-14"},{"Name":"Saveendra Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZd7txdrRe6l_t6due-EjqsvQvkp8RAB3UXUlYmpEDbtW_Gw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Birthday Dinner main course with a 12oz New York Striploin cooked to perfection served with tasty asparagus and yummy mashed potatoes. Complemented with 2 Servings of the Classic Margarita. Our Server was excellent and she topped it off with a complementary slice of Cheesecake. Fast Friendly Service with a smile. You have outdone yourself again Cactus. Cheers","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMfICdPqlopgvA2tAkHENDQvkdKkjzF0ti8RHye&fid=0x0:0x29de451081a450a0"],"When":"2024-6-11"}]

This is an eatery so inside of the restaurant is fulled of the food smell so we decided to sit outside. It was more peacefulüòó

The price of drinks are reasonable I think. This place is under new ownership and the food and drink selection is amazing! I had the Lamb pizza with banana peppers and it blew my socks off.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbeb7bdpCM18rPJAMln9LoOWzzu26H34fXr6PP&fid=0x0:0x842408b42802980e"],"When":"2024-10-6"},{"Name":"Jordan Ellis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6CEeIPS-loQURDvgAmkL1dRe7eqLm27RtfMqxJVA0n0p4cgv3=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Beanery is a hidden gem! [{"Name":"Veronica Flores","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXIcbpxxY7cEYQkV9Qidh7VmIOnFb2156UDhhTOBNCoTjA-Vac=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our dental team recently had the pleasure of experiencing the exceptional accommodations provided by Westwood Plateau and we couldn't be more thrilled with the experience. From start to finish, everything was perfectly organized and tailored to our needs. The staff went above and beyond to ensure our group felt welcome and well-cared-for. Their attention to detail and accommodating nature truly enhanced our experience. It was clear that they were committed to making our visit as enjoyable as possible. Overall, we had a fantastic time and are already looking forward to our next outing. We highly recommend Westwood Plateau for any group seeking a memorable and enjoyable golfing experience. Thank you Michelle for making our time so special!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Bernard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIHVVZffy0g5bV6LXjeZ74KJf8NsjvZc2kK4BLvlNCe0Pvn6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Golfed at this place for over 20 years and suddenly you can't hit drivers at the "driving range" even though it's never been an issue in the past. Save your money and find another one if you dare to want to use one of the funnest clubs in your bag. They say it's so "bc hydro workers might be hit" even though I've never seen one work the tower at the max possible distance a pro could hit the club. No tees and cheap mats make this a regrettable choice for a fun night testing your bag. Not to mention having someone just hired to watch you and make you feel uncomfortable just wanting to hit some balls.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPDMKkuk7fRpL7Xn0PtOr8vMWAq7gZOVEffIdXB&fid=0x0:0xab36c34c09dd5998"],"When":"2024-7-9"},{"Name":"dberN 93","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXe_7kptmUSVUSvtN7m5ewykhfQi21I5xcAmfY0iFgzRSbfbBg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Very fun casual golf experience.

The driving range is nice, you can order drinks and they have nice heaters if it gets cold. Only downside is you are limited to 250 yards.

The course is very fun to play, its an intermediate between a pitch and putt and full on golf course. A few short par 4s and a bunch of medium-long par 3s (115 to 185 yards). The main downside for me is the sand traps seem to receive little to no maintenance.

The staff are all very welcoming, generous and easy going. They make the experience even more fun.

There is also a BBQ outside with music and good hot dogs, which adds a great summer party ambiance.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJe2tooglWYypE3cK2gMIbwAO5O3gibXEvQYdDuXisb1j7wiw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Just had a great experience at this venue. People in the pro shop were super accommodating, friendly and knowledgeable. From being flexible with our booking in, to retrieving our left behind properly to helping out on apparel in the pro shop They are an absolute credit to the business. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaila Howard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUnwJ98owpkbOlLEdMzVHaQsqRezAt9Z0GHmAZy57HC7rhXEiK4Yg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"LOVE this course! It's so beautiful, with some incredible views along the way! The staff at the pro shop were amazing, so friendly and very accommodating. We were there a couple weeks ago and played through some crazy rain, one of my favourite days of golf i've ever had. Can't wait to play here again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eugene S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZk1vKJ1U5_8VNtqSIoRCc1gmtNBz_t1KtcH8dmyX1r-sI8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was at their training academy and it has a great setup. Really suitable for learning. Their cpga pro Ruel was super helpful and knows how to impart the golf knowledge to his students. Definitely a must try.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgVRtmLdPczH7Nlq2q53lgx-yg5bLD8oyUEywwI6nugax-q0JM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nice 12 hole course. Mostly par 3's but some par 4s. Can use a driver on about 2 or 3 holes. Some challenging shots. $20 to play on weekdays. Power carts are almost a must and they are $18 to rent. Very tiring to walk as it's located on the side of a mountain. At $20 it's good value. Will go again. Has a driving range, golf sims, and a full licensed restaurant.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPgJvbPxUAkVULxNYAZ6an7cRAkT5IydaGpv5Iz&fid=0x0:0xab36c34c09dd5998"],"When":"2019-8-30"},{"Name":"Paul Grimes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUh2dcV-KeKiiZJzAfq6rTrjExLXO2hA-dYeYoHESnAxCrNjy8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Staff are awesome. Very accommodating and friendly. The course needs a little work, but is a good 9 hole challenge.","Images":null,"When":""}]
