user_reviews: [{"Name":"Zeeshan Sohail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXQzSgXcEIo5d0fY039IL3LLi7k1i-9eyjB9u0xnur9BQekUdtD=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A decent upscale Syrian restaurant. The food and presentation are really nice and serving size is generous. The Lamb skewer and kababs are current favorites but we will definitely be coming back for more.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMAvckGfl0PoQUcUqY_W5zuNKxZrBZdZ3iBZKGw\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-9-10"},{"Name":"Neda G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcXBADLi2CMhn5hf9f-JdbOlYYM_LHhdjb9JmX03VjxzMph4k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I had high hopes for this restaurant as it is difficult to find an authentic Arabic Shawarma or Shish taouk in Coquitlam. But unfortunately, this wasn‚Äôt it. The atmosphere was nice and quite clean. However, the food and service not quite there. It took almost 30 mins for our food to come and sadly, two customers that arrived and ordered after us, received their food before us. All that aside, the sandwiches was what I was most excited to try. We ordered a beef and a chicken Shish taouk. The beef was quite smelly and I believe they cooked the chicken on the same flat top as the beef, and it smelled similar. Very small portion sizes for the price. The side of fries were also NOT authentic, they were Costco fries. We also ordered an appetizer of falafel, which was just ok. Overall, it did not meet or come close to my expectation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP1HMefI3ZmMv_z5j-__gdnwx2IpQObi9TKkOH2\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"M Ism","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIIouxyfjqFUskw-zPX-rf09-04JaS8UcC8StGLRfSFFg7FyQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"First time dining at the restaurant for a birthday celebration.  I must say the presentation along with the atmosphere was very nice.  The service was okay however, it seems that some of the servers did not have any experience.  The price of the food for what you're getting is unacceptable and not worth it at all.  We ended up ordering the family grill platter with assorted meats from the menu and it  was some of the driest meat that I have ever had.  The lamb, the chicken and beef were all dry and most of all flavorless.  The kunefe was OK and not the best.  The only thing that i could say was enjoyable was the bread and lentile soup.  I dont like giving out bad reviews but after spending over $200,  one would expect to get better food.  This will be the first and last time ever going to that restaurant.  I do not recommend this place at all. Looks good from the outside however overpriced and dry food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNJXbJMGqzFGiMxRFGwWS5nL58REzlIcfHvYXz2\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-6-24"},{"Name":"bahar n","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmfGtscBDa09dk7b-7RvVKIZH6hneZ4y0b-VObedbjnl-MZvE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Tonight, I went to Ayam Zaman restaurant for the first time. The shawarma had no meat and was just fat, and the food had a strong smell of lamb. The kebab was burnt, and when I mentioned the issues with their food, they said, ‚ÄúI will let the kitchen know.‚Äù The burnt kebab should have been replaced, as well as the shawarma, which was just fat. However, they didn‚Äôt do anything and gave no response regarding the bad food. It took them an hour to bring the food, and the food was terrible.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPt4dgLGQDg0BkBqsLuehEZZxmn8UW17fMSytSX\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-12-15"},{"Name":"Amitha Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU56Tb4Od8EpwDMLbqdGOzyvHJEOPTjgLc6IBJXDp0kdn-iBMY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went there for our anniversary lunch.\nBought a kebab plate and mandi. Everything was yummy but would have been better if kababs were served with hummus. It's a general Arabic practice. So was surprised when hummus was not given. Everything else was really good. The ambience and the investors were all great.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8Xyf_-_KUZaF4FlKfOmTWJV4NdOOrn_JYJGKA\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-5-28"},{"Name":"Cassie Meadow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWsGjxSINOhz43iQl213pjOWfdBb8gBCnc7FoXExHIIE0GlJImo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"saw some nice google reviews but was EXTREMELY DISAPPOINTED. hummus is actually quite nice but I thought my meal was a joke. I can‚Äôt believe I paid actual money for this. i‚Äôve had mana-eesh lebanese style pizza from other places and expected ground/minced meat and spices so ordered the sausage‚Ä¶. it‚Äôs HOT DOGS. I‚Äôm so mad about this but I guess they need my money more than I do if that‚Äôs what they are serving. The chicken shawarma wrap was probably authentic so it‚Äôs just a westernized preference of mine - though based on the description of sauce and pickles and based on the price I expected the usual wrap‚Ä¶ it was so small the width of a remote control and only seemed to have chicken inside. Sharing my photos so you are more informed than I was before deciding whether or not to purchase. again, really disappointing bc looking at other photos there might be some decent food here and I got very unlucky?","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPViF09VM2CFzCqMCgH1d3NTzsqlRUzTRuIldxW\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-8-6"},{"Name":"Linh Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbP3plInkqXVOA2XJc8czoQ80aWBGnT8WS-yMiUPgvNShtt-y90A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a great dinner. We shared falafel, beef skew \u0026 a chicken \u0026 beef platter and both were happy with the food. It seems to be an authentic Syrian restaurant as staff and most female customers wear head scarves. I assume you may not want to wear appealing clothes in this set up. The Arabian coffee was excellent, love it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNUsRgw3HmcwN5ov6tmszBiQXQ-EYISZD9CetPW\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-2-12"},{"Name":"Aisha Jiffry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpdLW73ITbiHPDEnII5e6j97XBkjReXwYhxebCypyTVxyiBmKqnQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We organized our company annual dinner over here. The service was top notch! Hats off to our servers and the food was really good! We were a group of twenty so had to book out the private room. It was spacious and clean! Loved the atmosphere. Overall had a wonderful experience and would return for more! I would recommend this place for families and they serve halal food!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile\u0026image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNg03q5uqulxKKIHnrftUrZNlx_DxvvXTKa2rXG\u0026fid=0x0:0xe28bd80ba773fc74"],"When":"2024-1-12"}]

They have different selection of Korean style of fried chicken. The Chicken soondal and monster green is our favorite. They also offer complimentary marinated white turnips on the side. I highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK_K1jrLJxFL7GhaFGtcCWZnWMLNFWPSY-th7a&fid=0x0:0xf02cfebfe9a5a06b"],"When":"2024-1-16"},{"Name":"Scott Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHpW7vGME__Zs4wKjXR04Upnw88bkVVyz-H2288JsHocq9vI3r=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I used to go here pretty often with friends before we go see a movie across the street. As for the food, I recommend honey garlic fried chicken and kimchi fried rice!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPpuLdsoRzvKhEeBcGXGDgCne4fL72fk9kxfs-Z&fid=0x0:0xf02cfebfe9a5a06b"],"When":"2024-1-23"},{"Name":"Dennis Li","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJgBHuKaxB6_AGRs3DyAn5DYWAJVYL8OdZQBLbOlZjEJJMR8F5KA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The $9.99 lunch menu has removed some items , added the corn chicken is for $12.95. I love it.

Will come back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ÏûÑÏßÄÌù¨","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHHbHVM7xbah01rMS3CXKtRLpC63-Qd0tzO9WR3gTLpDhm-g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was my first experience to this restaurant and I am never coming back. I would definitely return and have been telling my friends about this place.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuOU8FN1bJPscBDY3xO7XUXQcWxNd_0JIq9fZE&fid=0x0:0xf02cfebfe9a5a06b"],"When":"2018-6-14"}]

[{"Name":"karl tamondong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLLY0bDAwvCnz6iiK9JJS-w3hLSzr85XHvxgOGetYvjidzhcg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Great place to watch the game. Lots of TVs everywhere.

Just note

When you order wings it costs 50 cents extra to get your wings covered in the sauce or spices otherwise it'll come on the side and you'd have to dip and mix it yourself

Also refills aren't free they're $1 per refill.

Other than that my first visit was enjoyable","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTi7h3FcuLY4U9OVWDfeTAHUBDJ2NkayWR6bdV&fid=0x0:0xee6a49b8baf2cca2"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Antony Nemet","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpWKCwB0diWt-wfHCUSKBzVZvGKgsK2fD3w_KO1xqO1d58cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We came by today which is Labour day. Our waitress, Jill was exceptional. Her attentive to our table without being too repetitive was top notch. The breakfast poutine my girlfriend and I had was very good and the wings, delicious. I had the Thai ones which were basically amazing!! If you are looking for an awesome pub that hits the spot this is it. It was my first time here and will be my regular bi weekly choice.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMR-L40cVMpDajyg73z7gHRXmrdfEm--xogq_3D&fid=0x0:0xee6a49b8baf2cca2"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Patrick Chin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9837XYJatBhh8uygAXZ5cFqnhdVU7CsJgBMh-TzrJtW8lVns=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly staff. We got here early and found a cozy table. Our drinks were served almost immediately and our food came out almost immediately too.
The prime rib special was huge!!! And it came with a drink...
Highly recommended!!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOF-Jbcdqgbz0FVpvDE_t3n75W3KzOjtkROWkvR&fid=0x0:0xee6a49b8baf2cca2"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Lori Golden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6-VcfVSb5XiaNXuNybTZd8dFS8O8_6G4ifg6tWxwz1edWTIVr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We found this place because we searched for a great french onion soup in the Burnaby area.

Our server was amazing and friendly. She got to our table pretty fast and the place was full. We sure couldn't complain, she was prompt and very friendly.
Three out of the four had the French onion soup and loved it.
Drinks were good even though I ordered a Coors banquet, it's been years.
I highly recommend this place. If you want to catch a hockey game this place has you covered with tvs

[{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had the pleasure of trying Papa Leo‚Äôs in Coquitlam, and I have to say, it was an amazing experience. We ordered the pepperoni pizza and the double cheeseburger pizza, and both were absolutely delicious. The crust was perfectly baked‚Äîcrispy on the outside and soft on the inside‚Äîand the toppings were generous and full of flavor.

The pepperoni pizza had just the right amount of spice, with a classic taste that was spot-on. The double cheeseburger pizza, on the other hand, was a unique and delightful surprise. The combination of flavors truly mimicked a cheeseburger, and it worked so well on a pizza base. It was hearty, flavorful, and incredibly satisfying.

Overall, we enjoyed the pizzas very much, and I can confidently say that Papa Leo‚Äôs offers some of the best pizza in Coquitlam. If you‚Äôre looking for delicious, high-quality pizza with a variety of great options, this is the place to go. Highly recommended!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNt4QcZOduMQTw3ZQXg1q3amljQRFoCwubIjH0I&fid=0x0:0x3a98911e0346d378"],"When":"2024-8-11"},{"Name":"Christopher Friesen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1rXG18U1u8h-0EZ_3-VUL2AYdFt2RZkOdYaxB_cfCroMHJc9c=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Read lots of good reviews so my expectations were high but was left disappointed. $44 for 2 large couple topping pizzas, reg crust was undercooked and doughy while the thin crust was overcooked. Really nothing to complain about; my samosa chat was spicy, fine for me but might be too hot for some.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOjj0sceoYbyXO-EA9zyXRYQdykHMrISGmmnesq&fid=0x0:0xa85eb1513ae54e9f"],"When":"2024-7-20"},{"Name":"Harinder kaur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLvbgMs30RvntNtLqqRXDDHb0tkMY2d4jHkTvJrp1ndcDMuzA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I picked up  dry chilli paneer and onion Bhaji today at 11:37 pm. When I went home and opened it chilli paneer was with gravy . I called restaurant and  a girl sharan told us chef made it semi gravy for you. I told her but I order dry not with gravy or semi gravy then she told me nothing can be done, we will take care next time and then I opened onion bhaji half of the box was just onions no batter on them and was not chewable. I again called and told them I can‚Äôt eat this onion bhaji I will bring in your store and eat it and tell if you can eat it then she told me not to come today (12/18/24) come the following day. I said to her, but I take out food because I needed for the night not for tomorrow and she replied me again not to come.
This is not first time earlier also she refused to give me order as per the instructions saying we do not make tawa prantha‚Äôs here and never made before. But before I talked to her I always ordered tawa prantha‚Äôs once a week. After last month talking to her, she told she can‚Äôt make it. Or I would say it was already made dish they gave me. Because why would a chief will not follow the instructions? So disappointed I did made any fuzz about complaints I had before but this time was enough.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOHo9HoG1uAG47X4jhpO5lLl1vTS0hIr34yHzNI&fid=0x0:0xa85eb1513ae54e9f"],"When":"2024-12-19"},{"Name":"AYM Zeto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVz5GvKrEg3A0tbZbuO2ffKhkWqqqvubt9jM_ZmqmuBuntJI2W4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's a small place, take out only. [{"Name":"Vern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoBEa2DpCVgJo-G-26vwXXigumr7-aNIbPobMzYUx6xUys_Niz=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently dined at Narita Sushi and had an outstanding experience. The staff was incredibly friendly, attentive, and professional, making us feel right at home from the moment we walked in. The sushi was fresh and beautifully prepared, with a wide variety of options to choose from. The atmosphere was welcoming and comfortable, adding to the overall experience. I highly recommend Narita Sushi for anyone looking for delicious food and exceptional service. I‚Äôll definitely be coming back!

This review highlights both the quality of the food and the excellent service! Let me know if you‚Äôd like to add anything else.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPAU6DdLNeFolVYIv70lTuRxDohEikFtH4LzEOf&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-11-9"},{"Name":"Penny Rusty Sophie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkGfXMIDqwS_yD1axTk6tkHoLsnybE2ErvKrHMoMIElMJWekI_=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Visited Narita back in early September. Located in a fairly busy mini mall.

Ordered the following:
Salmon sashimi, gomae, agadashi tofu, chicken yaki udon, prawn tempura, and Narita roll.
I thought the sashimi was generously cut and the gomae was a good size portion. Also liked the Narita roll which had salmon, tuna, tamago, avocado, cucumber, and tobiko. It was a bit too covered in sauces but tasty nonetheless.

Overall, pretty good food here with fairly generous portion size.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPyJpH_p_awL96Lzgm9KbBWGY9CvvND1PN_UeIT&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-10-16"},{"Name":"liberty facundo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXNBp5rH1To4BVHWq1Mfj3iKJNDPtZ8CbWa3yq0RypDCjJicJtkRg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tried this place out for the first time and the food is really good. We ordered the dynamite roll, top gun roll, Takoyaki and they were quite filling. Will definitely come back again","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOs3jHqu1drOmHgZ63oOhOXztIp5n_kuPC-O_wr&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"inspiringfoodie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXzYkilODPLPrJrijGHIEENNuCPV7ORM1oJ-GQTIuFySkOHKAh2jA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Decided to try the restaurant on a Friday night. Surprisingly it was quite busy.

The ambiance is lacking & the restaurant is very small.

The food is okay some items are definitely better than others.

The Chicken Bento box was decent, nothing that would wow you, nothing that was disappointing.

One dish in particular that did not work for us was their sushi pizza. Normally sushi pizza is a must order for my partner so you know he had to try it here. It was the last dish that was served & unfortunately the most disappointing. While it was well presented, it was not a cohesive dish nor was it easy to eat. You couldn't eat it like a pizza. The Sashimi while fresh was cut too big for the pizza & while the bottom of the crust was crunchy the top of was soggy because of the imitation crab & the thick layer of mozzarella cheese.

The service was kind & friendly.

Maybe we just ordered the wrong things & it was an off night,  who knows.  Not sure I would give them another chance though.

@inspiringfoodie","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOxIZJc-NQ4amhcvCD7LOOSTro1lOluu-JrFRYh&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-10-26"},{"Name":"hungry dog","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUU9eKcRttu0wNDyfzMLCM37gn5w1HsQy-g0S0eoiVV9Pp_bIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"nice big portions at a reasonable price but tasted pretty average. the sashimi was nice and thicc and the sauce on that smoked salmon roll was so sweet that u wanrwd to chug water but the salmon saved u a little there. the tempura was crispy and avrg but they ley us replace all our veggies w „Åã„Åº„Å°„ÇÉ!! their rice to fish ratio was perfect too, rice wasnt too wet bit tasted like nothing, 3.8/5!!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipORYuKMxg7_6n45renLsaySEa4z4LFkaN0mGCyI&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-11-21"},{"Name":"May Zhagro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU9KviWdU_UGm6yjKPv-6aFaljm1EC_ecrxYhnt_LO3duiyBNho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba7-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"A small Japanese restaurant located in a plaza with all the other restaurants by the theatre and superstore. The menu is extensive and the price sure has increased a lot over the years. Luckily they still had the lunch special chicken bento box for $14 which is a good deal nowadays. It comes with marinated chicken in teriyaki sauce, sunomono salad, a spring roll, two gyoza, 8 pieces of California roll, and a miso soup. It was very filling and the ingredients are fresh. There weren‚Äôt too many seating but majority of the seats were filled during lunch time. Service was a bit slow for the seats nearby the door because the view for the server was not as straightforward as those sitting along the walls.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN53UJbEnsfmHxpCmgnbo9Y6jKwjgdox2jvB2w5&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-6-20"},{"Name":"Aidan Sweeney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuO1Y-vwcPiiu1ekNlIMvbPg8XKZQ8Ad74Kv8d8U6e9X8Mig=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Vegetarian friendly!

Good bang for buck! Thank you Narita Sushi!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOdMw_ZJmcUZf_1VekA_Hd8hcv6fIZRt0Zjs3A5&fid=0x0:0x6359c0d95e8de48f"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Kira Vurdela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLZ4ho8KhY9WNeG55Lsg7mZ46nw5wIxm7RngY4YrNfM5Q3ET_V=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very fresh sushi. All items were hot/fresh.
Yummy and quick. Left very satisfied.

(I think this location is much better/cleaner and has fresher food than the Comolake A&W).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOGTbaAkGCNscnyGTLhSc5DBuTz-4n3PiXWrtRV&fid=0x0:0x494ca6e88df63169"],"When":"2022-11-20"},{"Name":"Charmaine Wu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLk9kDTGufnwKJMg3Qq8m5I2ZIpk5ZNULOqkzx5aHbr_rnc5YU4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Breakfast has always been good at A&W and overall beats other fast food franchises as far as food quality and standards go, by far.  The staff are consistently friendly, and the sausage and egger on a regular bun continues to be a favourite! However, one thing the franchise can really stand to improve is it's iced coffee (and now coffee in general).  The low coffee quality sticks out like a sore thumb in comparison to all the rest of  the items on the menu, and though my partner and I love picking a&w as our go-to breakfast on-the-go, the iced coffee always disappoints and consistently lacks flavour, is way below average and really just comparable to a cup of water.  If the coffee were improved, A&W would win on all fronts and would continue to be our pick for a high quality and satisfying fast food breakfast spot!","Images":null,"When":""}]

Tasty sauces and toppings. Generous portion sizes considering the price‚Ä¶the Salt & Pepper chicken was especially large and crisp, and crunchy coating. Service was quick and friendly. Dining area was clean. Count me in for regular repeat visits to satisfy my constant cravings for hand pulled noodles!  Excellent noodle joint that also has offerings in Crystal Mall (Burnaby) and Continental Ctr (Richmond). Love it!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPsLjXKVj5DEZQheCIs65Egsww6E99zXtbIkQlE&fid=0x0:0x25dfa5714ccafc5d"],"When":"2024-11-14"},{"Name":"Jessy J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHNRFw0Z_JgaU0TxGr1Pv5X-w9V6JzR0bnCuTDlGr_7pfsbx_k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely must try and should you your stable food!

This place offers truly authentic Xi‚Äôan Chinese food. You can tell they didn‚Äôt cut any corners, from the marinating to the frying and stir-frying of the cumin lamb‚Äîit‚Äôs full of flavor and cooked to perfection. The hand-pulled noodles are a must-try, with a perfect texture that you won‚Äôt find just anywhere. The shredded potatoes are so light, you‚Äôd hardly think you‚Äôre eating potatoes, as the starch is minimal and the dish feels incredibly delicate.

The service is top-notch! From the warm greeting to expert menu recommendations, attentive tea refills, and thoughtful check-ins, the entire experience was seamless and heartwarming.

Parking can be tricky sometimes, but we had no problem finding a spot on a Saturday night!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNbgFglJr8AcF_s25w0qWaQeaRodunCkpj8UhI7&fid=0x0:0x25dfa5714ccafc5d"],"When":"2024-10-20"},{"Name":"Lee Hwan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6j8edfdMuAexJg284rJGK3C7SE7k9Zn0kKJfkMwoZJYiFzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Old Xian delivers an exceptional dining experience with authentic flavors and a warm, welcoming atmosphere. Everything here elevates the meal. Each dish is generously portioned, flavorful, and presented with care, showcasing the chef's dedication to authentic cuisine. The bold, unique flavors make it a standout destination for food lovers, and the reasonable prices only add to its appeal. I highly recommend Old Xian for anyone looking to explore rich, traditional flavors in a comfortable setting.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN_MAhMSr49wODWo1woIpfdP-MBvlqvyMm-SB-n&fid=0x0:0x25dfa5714ccafc5d"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"ÁøüÂ™õÂ™õ","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-kPaPCVBzNlAPdOSvP5Xl1gs9d1CJxju74RB4y__Cd8213g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The cold dishes here were fantastic! The flavors were rich and truly authentic, bringing out the best of traditional Chinese cuisine. Every bite reminded me of home, and the seasoning was perfect. If you‚Äôre looking for real Chinese taste, the cold dishes are a must-try!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOOG6rFxYhZNzQH7HAl84OBrRs7WjGD8cN-c7RC&fid=0x0:0x25dfa5714ccafc5d"],"When":"2024-9-16"},{"Name":"eric h","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4wiwKOOLAGG9P3k9zH8vSMybKZzZ7dkhejrfS-DBteL1ZiOwd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I‚Äôm not sure what went wrong, but the XI‚Äôan Hand-Pulled Noodles with Hot Spicy Oil was incredibly salty. I tried rinsing my mouth in the washroom, but the saltiness seemed to cling to my tongue. I‚Äôve never experienced anything like it. However, the waitress was very kind and took the dish off my bill, which I appreciated. Honestly, I‚Äôm only giving this place two stars because the service was good.

The first photo is the XI‚Äôan Hand-Pulled Noodles with Hot Spicy Oil.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNQoSf1RyhCSOs9Hz7S1NEhYJ1EPAaA1JGQmMyZ&fid=0x0:0x25dfa5714ccafc5d"],"When":"2024-8-31"},{"Name":"Tien Lam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXHCfEOuZX4sAnNQXCtC1HC1c_BtUEmjz0i2XKxPb_xq_Chxo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Good place for Chinese food. She brought the burger & fries on a tray that had Wendy's paper taped on the tray. The same tray & paper that she serve the food for all drive through customers. Very unhygienic. I will make a complaint with CFIA on Monday. Enough about gouging customers over bags & sacrificing hygiene over packaging material.
This non-sense has to stop. I will never go back to Wendy's again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Bisnett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaj0xmnuhDRnYOVeLcqjslTcMHMsm6NlCnjmlgl8yH-HZeBw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If your store chooses to open as late as 6:30 (should absolutely be earlier) then at very least be ready to serve food at 6:30.

Why did you choose to set up your business to waste my time like this? Do you want angry customers first thing in the morning? I am on my way to work and had to wait 8 mimutes in the drive through (0 other cars) just to place my order, then once i finally placed my order was reparked (again 0 cars) because your staff was not prepared to serve food.
You're holding up my day by being unprepared to serve breakfast at breakfast time. Fix this.","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Y S","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTmtWUtCZcs7qDdNKdjVbtcx5f5BcDfDU3YRp4zcFsXHKu1_WS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We came on a Saturday dinner around 6pm. The parking lot is very tiny and hard to find parking. There‚Äôs no other parking lot available nearby. The restaurant inside is spacious and the tables are not crowded together. The place can be noisy and I had trouble hearing what the person across from me was saying.

You order through a QR code and the food came very quickly. They have a small heat plate on the table to keep food warm.

Taste of the food was good. We liked the beef skewers. I don‚Äôt really like the tendon skewers because of the texture.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMm-pX5dlD9pMXI0FzAiGGywpJR6-RScI7s2spt&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-10-13"},{"Name":"Mathew Wong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqr0VMvVacTdghzD4J4MfAhe6q5dMZ1b1Ki5_SYoFGvzKwiW0B=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Delicious bbq skewers (pig skin, beef roll w enoki, chicken gizzard)and cold noodle. Service was great, atmosphere was good nothing fancy, my only issue was floor was a bit slippery, perhaps mop water was greasy and needs more bleach. I would come here again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHVW2maqSyKlLP-GolR3MZBsZ0g4sQoCvDBUw4&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-12-20"},{"Name":"Evan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItqym_b8p4Y-FW9783yYhbbkXgbWq5yo1i3Fyi_bB9_Q1tlIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I wanted to eat skewers one day and uh this spot like does the job. Me and my friend ordered like a bunch of skewers and they were good but not fantastic. I really liked the BBQ pork skewers and if you gk I reccomend gettin that one it was 8/10. The lamb , beef and tripe were only like a 6/10 . I will be back for more skewers and maybe tk try the other stuff. The price is like okay it's like 2 to 2.5 for skewers and uoh order through some random website on your phone .

Ps. They give you yummy chips to eat while u wait for the food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMGfGItpaqmbsJl5twz57dC541_7HO_VMMx7f22&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-30"},{"Name":"Y. Cherski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-7SLlKKRW0Rqcp9wRXFlvt6gbh0rtI7PMIroLgxETtGiPwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I was intrigued by the concept of this restaurant but felt the dining experience could have benefited greatly from the guidance of someone more seasoned. Navigating the menu was a bit of a challenge, as some choices seemed less substantial, leaving us wishing we had ordered differently. The menu's focus on meats was clear, yet a greater presence of vegetables would have been welcome, as we only stumbled upon the option for a salad after noticing another table enjoying one. Another quirk was the timing of the soup service, arriving unexpectedly at the end of our meal rather than at the beginning, well after all other dishes were served. While the bill can add up quickly, familiarity with the menu could indeed turn a visit here into a more satisfying and rewarding experience.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWH5sZ4xZB9c3y6UiKcGGnTPl9YW8md6Ua0hvi&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-5-7"},{"Name":"TERRY CHENG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsg-oI6sco7O5Go48_oGM2GdPS9ywAc_QfXDXDKM3uhrlF3VpMxg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If all the meat on a stick BBQ restaurant this restaurant is number one. The portions are more than other restaurants for the same price. The selection is also better than other restaurants and the most important the taste is far better than other restaurants. The staff has been amazing not just on occasion but every time I have been there. The beer is also cheaper than other restaurants too. The atmosphere is perfect for what it is, a wonderful place for friends or family. My only complaint is that there is only one men's toilet and one women's toilet.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNMSgMmyQX51QvFhlzC8JdU2dNxQPcdpRQafAIY&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-2-16"},{"Name":"Huang Recca","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDF647f8wTC9xYKRRSNQV8CPkQJrc1Y81nFNPZerRiknh_jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Used to be better but the standard seem to have dropped a bit. Some of the skewer arrived cold. Or overcooked. The lamb skewer used to be very good but today it seemed quite off. Portion of squid skewer shrank in size. Price can go up high if you dont watch what you are ordering.

Order via qr code using a smart phone. Some of the english menu appears to be done via online direct translation.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOm56CFLQnolpXXAW9_xZ5CDflNIGmIT_iBkCBx&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-6"},{"Name":"Kevin Kurniawan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwdtnJ5RbVf9X4FOyIvuW8Ujuf3XXqtUna-3fJWYoC7lMUEMXl=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Went here 3 times already. Food is great, service is also prompt. However with my last visit, which was yesterday, they served me one of the BBQ pork skewer which was undercooked.

I notified the staff, and what he did was just pulled away the rest of the BBQ pork skewers on our tray, heat it up again on the grill, and put it back.

Guy did not even say sorry, or take away the undercooked ones from my plate. Mistakes happen, but this is a very serious mistake. You don't want your customers to be ill after consuming your food.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP-wef92gFp2yzDJr9A3iqEtZxxYvJUjdR34VWj&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-8-19"},{"Name":"Triple Y","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpOUu3KPS1-er6yleoWeyiUKtsRw4U7A4457Dg5vEpOaOkhJ5E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The skewers were great, especially the lamb and beef. They were well seasoned. We also tried the cucumber salad, mung bean noodle and cold noodles. The service was the great, too! Highly recommend you to visit :)","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP4NpaspH8GH3T_Ikga4sqlPsl_2VGYFzUABcIn&fid=0x0:0x17360df85a1e9142"],"When":"2024-7-21"}]

[{"Name":"ÍπÄÌÉúÏö∞","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLsRamQI9udO7Ofboim5NFrvyyisl7xcYyYGr-glrF4xhGb1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"*OVERPRICED WITH LOW QUALITY*

We ordered a 14-inch Large Super Supreme Lover's pizza by Uber Eats and when we got the food from a delivery, we were baffled and disappointed in your food quality and visual of the pizza. First of all, the uploaded photo of the pizza from Uber Eats and the pizza that we got look so different. There were not enough toppings on the pizza compared to the image. Furthermore, they didn't even cut the pizza dough very well (it was just a whole pizza NOT SLICED) Lastly, the toppings were easily taken off from the dough so that whenever we tried to eat pizzas, we felt we were eating lasagna, not pizza.

We ordered this pizza by paying $51.49 (including taxes) and were so upset and disappointed in having this kind of low-quality and visual pizza. We'll never order pizzas from here again and shame on you.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoH3lr9rBEu_OeXScgZ_eKprmVtDteTBJAaku9&fid=0x0:0x2b20a5a20a9746d0"],"When":"2024-9-13"},{"Name":"Mahboubeh Soumeeh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWYDdZF0EYITzpASuc-GUgL3D-zOrPB5fdS08Hx_bFKpgbd83Da=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We ordered two different pizza. The solution he suggested was "order it extra cooked next time".","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ray R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXul9X_72hU3Tfw-HzmW64SPZHF56YyjvDgRJMA35qN0Rsv8UI7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"They always deliver to the wrong address. Pizza is great if you can find it","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Kerray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWstKt7tG-yuAbgC104e3a8f47n1rOsfU9W5Mf4nMEDoXnlInPI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"OK, that's it! I have ordered here many, many times and it's always the same awsome friendly service while upholding Pizza Huts standards. I recently ordered pizza for an entire baseball division for Coquitlam Little League and they got me the best deal they could, on time, hot and ready to go! Amazing   guys and thank-you so much!","Images":null,"When":""}]

[{"Name":"Sam Joshva Baskar Jesudasan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKLqS36N3NtQRA23Ww5QBrZV_otW4as2xzyiBtkdywx6CRIHc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I usually buy here everytime when I am in the neighborhood and gave them 4 star prior. But today I am totally disappointed with the service. We ordered 12 pieces chicken and paid extra for them to be breast meat and chicken sandwich for a total of around 70 dollars. The order was delayed which is okay. However the thing that is very frustrating and honestly unethical is 4 out of the 12 breasts is just bones. That is one third of the order being just bones.
We love church chicken. But today we are totally disappointed üòû. I have attached pictures to show how they are just too thin and bones compared to what they should be. This is very bad!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNTSNPUmUIEz6vwm5U56R1TOFWDTbD1tBAI6hA&fid=0x0:0x226ffdfb215f7f55"],"When":"2023-9-28"},{"Name":"Ryan Roulette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUUM8NIHV2-Utm1tuBMKuLVooVHig-eNGnSJqjxadsWoECegXpU9Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Unfortunately not the best experience at this location. Ordered a 4 piece spicy chicken combo and the chicken definitely wasn't fresh. I came around lunch time and was expecting better quality. It seemed as though the chicken had been sitting around for a long time. However, the biscuits are always good!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVujL3C7bQx17Az-mKA3VAnHoQ5YN1V_Eonn8UT9s-BNvSNbwS4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Ordered mexicana wrap and bbq sandwhich. After 15 minutes of watching other orders being taken without my order or any other in person order being fulfilled, I was finally told my order would be done in 1 minute, which was actually another 5 minutes. Once given my order, I checked (cause I watched him make it) and there was no bacon on the sandwhich. He then told me they have no bacon left. I told him I wasnt told there was no bacon when I ordered and I only ordered it for the bacon. After arguing with him he said he can give me bacon but in another 5 minutes. I gave up and left as I had already waited 20 minutes and watched him take 11 orders in that time, with none fulfilled that weren't online orders. He had a smile on his face the whole time which is a positive, but clearly not trained to deal honestly with the understaffed situation given to him.

When I got home I also discovered there was some ingredients missing in the wrap as well, as evidenced in the picture. Around 22$ for whats pictured here.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOXwats2TeNQTxxpX6w8hMesMIva3BeX9voFFag&fid=0x0:0x226ffdfb215f7f55"],"When":"2024-3-14"},{"Name":"Rick Kane","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFqClYvduB4zC0jsLgcciKEOlHUjk9_R9BcsbG_iB0-ZcHnnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Extremely slow. [{"Name":"Okpako Cyril","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVaNHZta1jM7gqQ_JUpXZci94qOXc8zdUCpiRKYiqYtGgVcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Hi Five Chicken today and had a great experience. The food was delicious! The chicken was crispy, perfectly cooked, and really well-seasoned. The place was clean and had a nice, welcoming vibe, which made the meal even better.
Service was a little slow, but that‚Äôs totally understandable since Zara is still training. She was so friendly and handled everything really well, she gave me something to chew before my order ready so I didn‚Äôt mind waiting a bit.
Overall, I had a great time at Hi Five Chicken and would definitely recommend it. Shoutout to Zara for doing such a great job.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOK1hVhWdT4U9NXbhjOhASrX40hlNgERtIZZUQm&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-4"},{"Name":"Andy Yu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9qg5Df2ZYSOWgUamBgaIFnvoNBzr4MYC3Em-ekQ3EO_Rv7Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an incredible experience at HiFive Chicken, all thanks to Rakhi! Her service was absolutely amazing ‚Äì friendly, attentive, and professional. She truly went above and beyond to make our visit memorable. Thank you, Rakhi, for your outstanding hospitality!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO5syUuNimI9ShvW7IrNlqc5RMWbEAxXXz4VVmq&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-24"},{"Name":"021 Rima Akter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpRbHZwUEZP3uYoGDv8yEC5E42IsVQEyVoc1nBO6tj0X-rKZDe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I‚Äôve been a regular customer here, and my experience has always been wonderful! The fried chicken here is always fresh, crispy, and absolutely delicious.The staff is consistently friendly and attentive, which makes every visit enjoyable.

Highly recommend this place for amazing food and excellent customer service. Thank you, Parneet, and the entire team for your exceptional service!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNmXcP1zehh0kJrZS3pP3m1qHxrz_4bX6zgHcnG&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-11-30"},{"Name":"Tannya Julieta Vasquez Barrientos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwq4ZPOvl-CKsAHqUINO4rrIpNESx_wX4Yl0iC0EmnT2wQBf4e=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The food is very good, especially their sandwiches. The fried chicken combos are the best, and the extra crunchy fries are amazing. The service is truly incredible. They help you choose your menu if it‚Äôs your first time there. I would definitely go back to this place. Bonus points: you can play Street Fighter arcade!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOfsvW-wAweAy4K9lc_1hQ5IqfATtGs9Vnv6sia&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-2"},{"Name":"Razaul Rezvi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCmfltE13lupE0zk9NLPPvL2aUV0qFGroVaRQDYg3Dc4qacQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I had a terrible experience at this fried chicken place. I ordered a fried thigh, and it was hard, greasy, and smelled awful. It seemed like it was either days old or fried multiple times. The staff were unhelpful and defensive when I gave them feedback, insisting they always cook fresh food, even though I showed them the disgusting chicken.

When I asked for a replacement, the staff said it would take 30 minutes, then changed to 20 minutes, and finally said 13 minutes after checking the oven. Clearly, they don‚Äôt care about providing good customer service. They refused to give me a refund, and I had no choice but to accept two drumsticks instead of the thigh I originally ordered.

If you buy chicken from this place, be cautious. If it looks red like in the picture, do not buy it‚Äîdemand a replacement. If it‚Äôs soft like the drumstick, then it‚Äôs safe to buy. This was a very bad experience, and it‚Äôs unfortunate because it‚Äôs my second time dealing with this. Last time, I arrived at the store to complain, but it was already closed. I hope they improve, but I won‚Äôt be coming back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMKtW3HEtXwcnyez8WHmOPC7sAmXcAtG0t5VzEd&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-7-4"},{"Name":"Paul Afuto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVswcrHR4BuJWVdul9Az7Mss_8tRmCXwFULcVSaUvDMFvbrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at this Hi-Five. Definitely my favourite throughout the lower mainland. Was serviced by Manpreet Kaur who went above and beyond for us. Clean and welcoming environment with games to play and all. Definitely recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPbNAFaLYClsZIEiSMj-BR3xSo0NcjUycx5f6fJ&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-12-17"},{"Name":"Bobby Bhinder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXFML71qLNE7mZP5JrN6_ihKr8qgI_idGbKQXHKs1WszTkagLhn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Prices charged, not as advertised.  Had to point out mistakes to get corrected.

Staff is very nice but missing spoon with coleslaw so had to eat it with the lit , my makeshift spoon.

Requested the chicken meal without  drums and was told it was not possible but will see what he could do.. gave me 2 drums instead..

Chicken was greasy as expected, otherwise cooked. Added a pic of the one thigh I received of a 3 pcs meal besides the 2 drums

I received only one thin napkin, a bit pricy for what you get, a little disappointed, will not be visiting again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMtGoVb7vdMl0gdRkQeyQ-qfuOHnfN5cxeAWRgG&fid=0x0:0x224de8ba58afb063"],"When":"2024-10-3"},{"Name":"Day Seize","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7pyDpYQ-O3mZSb0nH3LYIRDmLb6oS5KUInureHLnFD3zmYA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff Mohit is very friendly and has good service. [{"Name":"Chris Cordova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZBfclXmtbmhhB8FvSMIZiTpi-DgH3t2D-yb9xJsLbNeGaHg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don't be confused when you come in, but there are two restaurants sharing the same space. Today I tried Santo Remedio. I went with the Burro Suizo with chicken pastor and loved the authenticity, and freshness of the food. The chips and salsa were a nice touch. They did say to be careful with the hot salsa, but I was able to tolerate it well. Service was friendly and welcoming as well.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMkzpeXw7dP5enSc0RVz0XMmJZMPQwkme1isZo&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-10-22"},{"Name":"Tyler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX5pgqDcV4jXxCDs44gFpKqBE7-kpDe9pqH0qySpykt9h70rZWn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I recently visited Santo Remedio in Coquitlam and had a delightful experience. The Quesabirria was absolutely delicious, bursting with rich flavors and tender meat that made it a standout dish. We also tried the churros, which were perfectly crispy on the outside and soft on the inside, making for a fantastic dessert.

The customer service was commendable; the staff were attentive and friendly, ensuring we had everything we needed throughout our meal. The overall atmosphere of the restaurant was welcoming and comfortable, contributing to an enjoyable dining experience.

In conclusion, Santo Remedio offers great food and good service, making it a solid choice for a meal out. I'd rate it a solid 7.8 out of 10 and definitely recommend giving it a try.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPuQVGN274buBSImwoCqtniV7Ons4ciFVNa99KO&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"MC HK","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRdPoAKEhQfRTjiiusyGNXr5Ly2c8eFi51iorP25Zmt8NbZjYp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is a hidden gem!  Authentic Mexican street food place.  Loved their food, especially the Nachos and Tortas.  It is connected to a bowling lane/arcade so my kids loved it here. Highly recommend.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPJ9WjRl0t56hL7ysOpyNqXiS277oelXQj3LoQ4&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-7-2"},{"Name":"Mounota","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvpiSPg9AtpTNs-8JJvoJHojdmAI1FZcME9pprQbBKumVFhadS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"they gave us free tortilla chips with dips. the birria tacos were great. the margaritas were great too üíï the service was welcoming! will most definitely come back ü•∞","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO6qzimmSFEA027d1nd_QI9An99iaUvCGJzjJvz&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-11-20"},{"Name":"Aaron Reynaldos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMzJe1eszFpqbclLbMJev3bNCsQAmeHjm-xukVjqhBSbq_Ds1WiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great place for authentic Mexican food. The tacos are amazing, flavourful and in good portions. The quesabirrias and the broth are on spot. If you are looking for great tacos, this is the place. They have other options on the menu, like quesadillas, gringas and tortas.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMel6MR4xMqKfyjREbt6uS4MpXjPwUMRZga7v4c&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-8-27"},{"Name":"Sian Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXn_28uZIG3wyqyiqji_7ln4fQBQrfpYa8ayycWWZJpnK3MXkMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Quesabirrias are incredible as well as the tacos!! Service was great, you can tell they put a lot of effort into their food. 10/10","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNjbEyf9mUSVhroGx-tvdlirEWKfO4Uj2xesRaV&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Brandon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWE5ylqIqhNC5HK953SI2cXCmh8o4XQmXRGak1fjTx9ajXPFO0z=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"Pretty good. A couple of issues I had:
1. Meat was dry, but the flavors are there.
2. Guacamole (Wakaguac) - didn't really have much flavor and was a little watery.

The good:
1. Salsa and Pico de Gallo are very tasty
2. Double corn tortillas for the tacos
3. Service is super kind and friendly
4. Flavors are great, but the dry meat is a killer

I know they just opened and are getting into the groove of things. I'll definitely try this place again.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNHV5Qbu_jp0Q8FRmDA1FNZQmLEquz1BU8bQ7qI&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-6-13"},{"Name":"Adaio Spathelfer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKK3R1ZCU-pNloADThCyb1Kcd7NkD7jCl94lxmMOMIWUltjNw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great food, great service, thankful to have good Mexican near me and my family. Highly recommend, always looking forward to their chorizo tacos with a coke","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgCnMGUmGuuikSVq2rnDGbAcM7vYS13MrP0EMW&fid=0x0:0xcf2a45f8395b0cc5"],"When":"2024-10-13"}]

[{"Name":"n w","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7UQDByN6t0nePZ4CYWGH0Dj4t17qJ_wKRbK-ykQWwq7mgd96m=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I‚Äôve ordered from this location before and have had good experiences. However, I took advantage of the Canadian pizza promo for $10 and was disappointed at the lack of toppings. The pizza was supposed to have extra pepperoni but there was literally 1 or 2 pieces on each slice. The ham was lacking as well, just one pieces on each slice.

I understand that I cannot expect too much for $10, but clearly the savings resulted in a less than stellar product. Had I known I would get less toppings, I would‚Äôve ordered a pizza at full price.

I‚Äôve ordered promos from pizza franchises and I‚Äôve never had the quality drop off this much. I love pizza so it takes a lot for me to complain.

I would recommend ordering from Dominos‚Äô everyday special deal for $12 if you‚Äôre looking for a better quality pizza. [{"Name":"Pam Delfino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVou97WNj_X-lZ_I6WAUZr7ELzzqVVEd-LYy7ydp9dEDslErRA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a lovely dinner with my family at this pub! Very tasty food and fantastic selection of craft beer! I was so glad to see Fat Tug on tap! ‚ù§Ô∏è","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMCw6OeZ8D1RdzXcp-ow4tpv8BGwB1SaHRKk6GH&fid=0x0:0xe9fe07b789c02baf"],"When":"2024-10-21"},{"Name":"Grant M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRWL_i5cZiVpXExK1H8xMkwx4_6CHC_xRkP2HoYZIVJehiW1g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's been a while since I've been to the John B Pub, a friend of mine and myself decided after a few years to go for lunch.Sure glad we decided to go to the "B" The food in the past has always been so consistent and very good. And happy to say after a few years it's still the same ( absolutely consistent )

We both had the JB Bacon Double Cheese Burger, with me having the Onion Rings, and the friend of mine the Fries and a Gluten free Bun for him as well.

Burgers were outstanding and extremely flavorful and definitely fresh, Onion Rings and Fries were both on point also. Add a couple beers to everything... And perfect...!!!

Service was very good, and our server always came around to see how we were doing.

Now that many of us are retired early now, we all may be going to the John B Pub more often for lunch.

By the way the menu has so much to offer, and covers everyone's needs. Seems like they downsized the menu a bit, because I definitely remember it being so many pages to turn lol. It was almost too much to choose from before. Now it seems to be the perfect menu size, that still covers everyone's needs.

Cheers will be back...","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNCIl5weyZfy-tbWvpkv0HWxhERz2VZD1NmiBco&fid=0x0:0xe9fe07b789c02baf"],"When":"2024-11-15"},{"Name":"A Miraji","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKbtSn1-d3iEkTDQas0xH_xCGg1PKv8z1hKaZIhPkrsgM_kICp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best place to hit especially Friday nights while they have In house DJ or live music. Food and drinks are awesome and the staff are super nice and helpful.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOAjCww_Obs6VvTLfdD5WOpuQgId9G8YOKNpqN_&fid=0x0:0xe9fe07b789c02baf"],"When":"2024-12-11"},{"Name":"Munro Stuff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWj0Wcuk6ox5dfAeJ4fAaMbhX_F-nzzt3p5oc_f0hBd0NpbGSM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"It was okay, nothing fabulous. Salmon bowl was pretty good. Chicken club was delish and so was the soup of the day (beef barley). But the $2.75 upcharge for anything other than fries is atypical and a bit much. They don't do tasters "because they have so many beers" - uh, that's exactly why you should do tasters (like every other place), but you could make a limit of 2-3!?! It took two requests and nearly 45min to get water. And the server brought a different 'beertail' than the one I ordered, which I only noticed on our bill (also nearly half are actually 'cidertails'??). Not rushing back.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPu9thI15-mPT1SvaAw9VC9LFt-dae2bkeZwxH2&fid=0x0:0xe9fe07b789c02baf"],"When":"2024-8-7"},{"Name":"Zakk Flanagan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU73mUuM-1HHbf1A2-tTxkzpzu_k_ERm0No0wX5pr8S1D4_JXMB=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"The food is good, love the steak.  Happy hour offers good choice and always a wide range of drinks to choose from.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMMGPh-_jPI0jAYa24nSYsF1Y-0av8I51YP970O&fid=0x0:0xe9fe07b789c02baf"],"When":"2024-9-2"},{"Name":"Ms. Fancy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXBQaNfblq64oqWShq2FuM-_BC-1ScwkOJu_eYkfqvQy0DjNuPb=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Enjoyed my visit here yesterday.
Our server was mostly attentive, and the atmosphere was good. I appreciate that the music was low enough for casual conversation.
The salt & pepper wings were crispy and flavorful, the garlic prawns cooked perfectly and my guest's meal (Pad Thai) smelled divine!
I would love to return to sample other dishes here!

Ms. Fancy

[{"Name":"Jessy J","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHNRFw0Z_JgaU0TxGr1Pv5X-w9V6JzR0bnCuTDlGr_7pfsbx_k=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"On time pick up. I would say the quality and price are in good correlation. We got a super family pack with a large pizza and 2 lasagna/spaghetti and garlic toast and 2 pop for 2 adults and 2 kids and we have enough food for 2 meals.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMWbNb9DlFB-ZHF14W3aE13XWJELjFkou3NkB5x&fid=0x0:0xfe18f4076234865c"],"When":"2024-4-22"},{"Name":"Yun Son","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGjgi_ufk8MietM6eJ7yD4p_OdRl-a72wdZyC67MNi60YXbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow, this has got to be the best local pizza I ever had. The pizza was perfect, the crust was nice and tasty and the amount of topping was nothing but generous. Props to the guy that made my pizza. The only downside is how soggy the pizza can get. The sheer amount of topping does create a lot of water, so its hard to eat it without the entire top falling off. But it was definitely not a problem for me. I enjoyed every bite and would definitely recommend this place to anyone else","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Stevens","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6tYT8iCj-TAdoipwI6NcZVkXjE_HLPd6TbIV1_kaZjvnQSS4N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"First time using these guys. I even called in and told them I was going to do a google review after we get the delivery. So the presentation was good.. then it was time to eat the food. First I took a bite of the chicken wings.. they seemed to be dry. The hot flavor was good.. now the pizza! We ordered two pizzas, one was pepperoni, hot ham " which is hot btw" and bacon. The other was hamburger, onions and fresh green pepper. They were skimpy on the pizza sauce, the dough was great not too high and chewy. Now the topping were skimpy as well.. My suggestion is order extra pizza sauce. Next was the lasagna, it was watered down and noodle were soggy! For the price of $37.00 it's not bad, but beware of the quality","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMpOCLwP7E0YSiScjSk4c9vH7tzENLZd6UHayUX&fid=0x0:0xfe18f4076234865c"],"When":"2020-2-5"},{"Name":"WHV WHV","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDlwMNTWy3H2hK42K39MeFUB9-83h5T1AhNFNe6kVB-AgQeg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We went there for the pizza the first time after seeing many good comments about their pizza. However, all of us were disappointed. We order two large pizzas for special. The pizza was overwhelming salty. I also concerned about their hygiene after picking up the phone for the order then back to make the pizza. The only positive thing I could think of is their pizza is slightly cheaper than other places...I would rather to spend a little more money for something else for a better tase and services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Minwoo Choi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEyGT2eKDP8MdGRBIZosuoXJ6chgtevqB58lvqiFLOZLtmWZhU=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Price: Awesome!
Appearance: Awesome!
Taste: Amazing and delicious!
1/2 Garlic Vegetable Pizza
1/2 Garlic Chicken Pizza

To the owner, sorry and forgive me, I have been around in town for awhile but this was the first time I purchased pizza from over here.
After eating here last night, I am deleting and getting rid of my account record from all other pizza chain places. You will be my one and only from now on for takeout pizza (As long as I am residing in this town).","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMnu7Yybw34fWeYnEmsBD7LpljHPatkQTi8tTj2&fid=0x0:0xfe18f4076234865c"],"When":"2022-2-10"},{"Name":"C P","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVSWAbs1Uw6Hil8qAe5awirIqlg2bt-F94Nb0sjeWeC8xMp0fkK=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Picked up 2 large üçï pepperoni and cheese! [{"Name":"Arcadia Phon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7bMMBAuYvTpvuK0CVK85SPnFvDe3hVlD3cBfscG30U8JU_Ho=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A nice small cozy place for high end sushi. Their special rolls and oishi in particular are special. If theres a down side, it would be they have limited seats and no AC in the restaurant. But aside from that most of their special rolls are torched where you can see them torch professionally if you dine in.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipO8lx3l-3bYRkfiNj3JBdFLR7312JFvgqC9mvTy&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2024-8-13"},{"Name":"Justine H (Sunny)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmvMXm-P_-zaDju2DtLb4mJNuo8OiXNtbw6zPhVOcICWtiAOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great and quiet place to eat alone or with 2-4 people if you guys are looking for a really cozy restaurant. Since the place is so small, it is easy for them to watch over you and provide good service but it might not be best if you want to eat with a lively large group, as it may feel cramped or awkward. The atmosphere is very peaceful and I like the soft music they play. I recommend their special rolls. There's a great variety that are all very tasty. They do offer some other dishes like ramen and dons but I'd say I'm much more likely to come here again for just the sushi. Overall, hada pleasant experience :D","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOgfLbsuWiREQhG1bgOpa5IkV30IEGmnoBhL37r&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2023-12-23"},{"Name":"Lori Golden","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV6-VcfVSb5XiaNXuNybTZd8dFS8O8_6G4ifg6tWxwz1edWTIVr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We always love eating here each time we are on the mainland.
Best sushi we have ever had, fresh and amazing. Service is top notch and always friendly.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNFbAsensJt792kPExAHw4EJ8iCXxb6PyGdxHxB&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2022-7-11"},{"Name":"Elmira Nazari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUS8psOPde-fgvVYsglTVKj-j9hpNdB1347mGr_T9d11yAStREO4w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This little sushi spot was delicious. The salmon aburi was such a unique and tasty one. The prawn tempura is made with a different type of batter that is different than most sushi places but really good. The special rolls are good but felt like they are missing a bit of flavour. Overall great spot to try something new in the japanese/sushi cuisine. Good service as well!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPaxy7PIBUjMozDVsECnzl-ksmE2-VLpnoMzmYY&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2023-4-23"},{"Name":"Vic Yung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJjSUFpvFSwHsCrywPzGZzN7WDhV8Ljlj3YECw07iwjqMR_leW5=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went on a weekday evening and the place was empty. We were seated right away and got to pick our table. The space itself is rather small with enough room for about four tables. The place where the sushi is prepared runs adjacent to the tables in a bar format with a kitchen for hot food further inside.

Staff were patient in waiting for us to peruse the menu and order and took the time to read our order back to us to make sure they got it right. Sushi was prepared upon ordering and you could see some of it being made from the table.

Presentation of each dish was clean and simple. All the fish was very fresh and each piece held together when picked up. The rice was also well-made.

Price is similar to other independent sushi places in the area. Would recommend for a quiet place to eat with a small group of people or on your own.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipONDZld4lnBJmkeu8lBa2gT1OfT70PHuzTEYkQB&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2023-4-22"},{"Name":"Christine W","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWKPsEE58m4l7C5YBEcOPLQtBTaYwdBFGzTSKEIraaLnCr6OYcs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I came here with my close friends (there were 9 of us) on a Saturday at 3pm as I saw that there were really good reviews.

The place itself is really small and we took up half of their occupancy space but it was during a quiet time and there was only one other table finishing up.

We let our teenagers order first since they were hungry and we want more time with the menu.  My friends and I ordered 2 rounds of 2 large Asahis that were ice cold and refreshing.

We ordered the parents‚Äô meals shortly after although it took a while for the server to take our order and she walked away before all of the adults could order (she only took 2 out of 4 orders).

The first round of food for the teens came out in a timely manner but our food took an extremely long time. We also had to ask for soy sauce, wasabi and ginger, they did not come on our sushi plates.

We were there for almost an hour before we got our food.  There was only one chef making the sushi and I assumed it took so long because we ordered the torched and specialty sushi.

The wait was worth it though - the Volcano roll was absolutely delicious, among the best specialty rolls I‚Äôve ever had.  The Oshi salmon sushi was okay.  Everyone else really enjoyed their meals.

Even though our food took so long, we didn‚Äôt make a fuss about it and had a great time.  However, we had only finished our meal 15 minutes before the server told us that we needed to leave for the next guests.  We apologized and left but were really put off by this.  There was only one table for two that came in the entire 1.5 hours we were there and there was still another table for 4 empty.  No take out orders were picked up during that time either.

We stayed outside of the restaurant for another 30 minutes socializing with our friends and no one came in so it was odd that they told us to leave. Again, this was during a quiet time at 4:20pm when we were told to leave.

The food is great, but not the friendliest service unfortunately, hence the 3 stars for service.  The server almost seemed annoyed when we first came in and told her we were a party of 9 and when we asked her for the ginger, wasabi and soy sauce.

The bill for our family of 5 came to $120 and we got 2 rolls for each kid, a prawn tempura, 2 nigiri salmon sushi, a volcano roll, a salmon oishi, and 2 large Asahi.

Bottom line, yes I would recommend this place for good, fresh sushi but be aware that there may be a seating time limit even if they take a long time to get your food out and there are no guests waiting for a table and the server is not friendly and made us feel unwelcome.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPKwXerCD0i2Kk5Me-1YG5NfRuiKA89k6wCgt3R&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2023-11-5"},{"Name":"Ads","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwDyuvQtXP_VygmU1rNXhUJ0mc48E4h1QtDkdEfrlXmuS-mYhL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba8-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"This is a quaint, family ran operating local business by a lovely couple. A very authentic sushi joint with indoor dine in and easy takeout options.
We got the Party Tray A & C which was more than enough sushi for eleven people for lunch. The tray was delivered beautifully, excellent presentation and tasted absolutely delicious. Very fresh, unsalted super yummy sushi and you can tell the chef is very talented with a lot of pride put into his efforts.
The trays were more on the expensive side in comparison to other places, but you absolutely get value for money with this sushi joint and I would definetely choose to eat here again.
Support local! Please order where you can directly via the restaurant to stop third parties from taking all the commission.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPHWYV1wQa_T6im4C_ng01zYS6HZuiAGw-A9fyX&fid=0x0:0x3ffd3bcec282eb32"],"When":"2021-5-31"},{"Name":"Selena Jamie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3tWtt6PnSTFx_XvNEAakqyJI7cSRi4CXxeu0TjR0EDaooGUOnWg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Server was great, chef was personable and the food....was amazing , see my photos! [{"Name":"Paulo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJLcA_plm7bkWjnqTJrnEsHhDOSAcI0Thh-Pnw_Wtq2KxuMbiQFg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've passed by this so many times not knowing what it was.
Their reviews are really good.
Finally decided to check it out for myself and this place did not disappoint.

Their ramen was really full of flavor.
The smoked pork was really delicious.
I had the spicy ramen at medium heat, next time I'll try it at the spiciest heat level, then also try the spicy cheese ramen and the boneless chicken.
The atmosphere and setting is really cool.
The staff (he) was really cool too.
Will def come back here again!

My only complaint would be I wish they had some Korean drinks/beers.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMHIG6wJVcQLDYQ7fWFB7e6tVnpou2Hn4VujJwV&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-12-13"},{"Name":"Milad Hakimi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJS3tct7xdR_FQg-khxqYfaH1AaaOQttjGkVsM1Uxloq07E-lf=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We got the smoked pork belly and the regular ramen and they were fantastic!
Also I loved the soft noodles. They‚Äôre much better than the chewy ones I had elsewhere.

Definitely will come back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipN6pdHHXNBI3xPyFjbzvFC5EqeUzZH6kNuWo_WV&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-9-22"},{"Name":"Patty B.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXkD4op5IclLwtyGld7EArEDA0uGPTId3d9EWMFqyBZhH5FvL8b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We discovered this ramen spot through Google, and we‚Äôre so glad we gave it a try! Otherwise, we might have just kept walking past this hidden gem. It‚Äôs a great reminder not to judge a place by its exterior üòù.

Our favorite ramen spot has always been Honjin Ramen, but now this place has earned a spot on our list. Whenever we‚Äôre craving something spicy, this is where we go. We always order their Spicy Ramen but stick to the Medium Spicy option since it can get quite intense. The ramen has a unique flavor with a Korean twist, and it‚Äôs done so well‚Äîthe flavors and aroma blend perfectly.

We‚Äôre also big fans of their Takoyaki. Just a heads-up, though‚Äîit‚Äôs super hot on the inside, so handle with care! Thank you for serving such amazing food. We‚Äôll definitely keep coming back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNoRoYSUtN1oVG2r8rNjdamRdr2vYc5LhslYEPG&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-11-22"},{"Name":"Meredith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtIhmRfKvKapzOH3Jh8_o3LvCuX7OoNsQCsk7xHgvu0tUTt3o7=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Exterior is very unassuming, menu is simple which I personally prefer and the service was quick. The pork belly and ramen had many levels of flavour and was absolutely delicious. I will definitely be back!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipPxtHNPyh8fyBtLRVCUSGWVYF6wIYqpMKPbW5gB&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-8-5"},{"Name":"Yumi Chung","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPFqDkxESWXC88SASBBMb5TodqjqiFWci9IiQVgmoclWTpAqs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Smoking pig aka ramengers- Cute little ramen spot in Coquitlam area. We tried their spicy ramen (mild level spice) and really enjoyed it. The chashu  was really tender and tasty, noodles had a nice bouncy texture and, broth was not as salty so it was nice to drink. Honestly, a pretty solid bowl of ramen. Down to try their gukbap next time. They also offer free serve yourself kimchi on the side, which I actually enjoyed quite a bit.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipP8n9fE6w2-vtJxTThr1Vy5KEMcEqEY4mEbsBOi&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-9-21"},{"Name":"A.J. Canadian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU0mITu_1OR_MuXzhVIkPjHjZnimy2Y-mI64r72OA1Zbucah6-N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Coquitlam's own Smoking Pig ramen restaurant. You have to try the delicious homemade ramen noodles dishes to experience. I love the decor and aesthetic as well. Where else could you enjoy comic book posters, video games, collectibles and models as you wait for your food. I loved to play classic arcade games on the multi game arcade cabinet. No reservations, first come first served. Recommended","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipOTJFHUk7lXF1iKVfbuWKiBy6ed1rROg4UzK42x&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-7-13"},{"Name":"AJ Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsu0-zLfdBIi0BMvFkmCrQ7LvpDpcqpsmyMO44b1viyR7y0ygy=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"Quirky ramen spot with a LOVE for Marvel! Great ramen with amazing smoked pork whose flavour was out standing. The noodles were a bit different than most places but still really good.

Music was a plus, great playlist that just fits the vibe!

Parking is a little tight though so be aware before you arrive.","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipMaLROeaK6ohawFwgkWlEVtuInCuP_1-bQQ45d8&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-6-23"},{"Name":"Jay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpO4Bh8DZWAUVAzJ_hJYjoLutXZbl0vSp4y69d3OqZWEClfNlh=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best ramen spot, hands down! I've tried so many places, but nothing compares to this one. Seriously, top-tier ramen. I first tried it last year and now I go almost every other week! If I lived closer, I'd be here twice a week for sure.

Perilla Ramen, Spicy Ramen, Spicy Perilla Ramen‚Äîeverything is amazing, but the Spicy Perilla Ramen is the ultimate winner! The decor is super cool with Gundam figures, Avengers stuff, and even a little arcade machine (bring some coins). The service is great, and the owner and his wife are super friendly. Absolutely recommend this ramen gem!","Images":["www.google.com/local/imagery/report/?cb_client=maps_sv.tactile&image_key=!1e10!2sAF1QipNWqVgpoNd-kKKnt6p4FtvUCnoPOIKi3JPP_XNZ&fid=0x0:0x1d20f0214579bd6"],"When":"2024-8-10"}]
